# <a name="sensitive-information-type-entity-definitions"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-104">機密情報の種類のエンティティ定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-104">Sensitive information type entity definitions</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-105">この記事では、すべての機密情報の種類エンティティ定義を一覧表示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-105">This article lists all sensitive information type entity definitions.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-106">各定義は、DLP ポリシーが各種類を検出するために検索する情報を示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-106">Each definition shows what a DLP policy looks for to detect each type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-107">機密情報の種類の詳細については、「機密情報の [種類」を参照してください。](sensitive-information-type-learn-about.md)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-107">To learn more about sensitive information types, see [Sensitive information types](sensitive-information-type-learn-about.md)</span></span>

## <a name="aba-routing-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-108">ABA ルーティング番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-108">ABA routing number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-109">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-109">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-110">書式付きまたは書式設定されていないパターンに含め得る 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-110">nine digits that may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-111">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-111">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-112">00 ~ 12、21~32、61~72、または 80 の範囲の 2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-112">two digits in the ranges 00-12, 21-32, 61-72, or 80</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-113">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-113">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-114">オプションのハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-114">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-115">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-115">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-116">オプションのハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-116">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-117">数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-117">a digit</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-118">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-118">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-119">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-119">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-120">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-120">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-121">ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-121">A policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-122">関数 Func_aba_routing がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-122">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-123">Keyword_ABA_Routing のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-123">A keyword from Keyword_ABA_Routing is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-124">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-124">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-125">関数 Func_aba_routing がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-125">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- ABA Routing Number -->
    <Entity id="cb353f78-2b72-4c3c-8827-92ebe4f69fdf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ABA_Routing" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="argentina-national-identity-dni-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-143">アルゼンチンの国民 ID (DNI) 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-143">Argentina national identity (DNI) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-144">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-144">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-145">ピリオドの付きまたは指定のない 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-145">Eight digits with or without periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-146">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-146">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-147">8 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-147">Eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-148">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-148">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-149">オプションの期間</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-149">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-150">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-150">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-151">オプションの期間</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-151">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-152">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-152">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-153">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-153">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-154">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-154">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-155">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-155">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-156">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-156">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-157">正規表現は、Regex_argentina_national_id一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-157">The regular expression Regex_argentina_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-158">このページのKeyword_argentina_national_idが見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-158">A keyword from Keyword_argentina_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Argentina National Identity (DNI) Number -->
<Entity id="eefbb00e-8282-433c-8620-8f1da3bffdb2" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_argentina_national_id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_argentina_national_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_argentina_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-160">Keyword_argentina_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-160">Keyword_argentina_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-161">Argentina National Identity number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-161">Argentina National Identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-162">cedula</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-162">cedula</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-163">cédula</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-163">cédula</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-164">dni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-164">dni</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-165">documento nacional de identidad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-165">documento nacional de identidad</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-166">documento número</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-166">documento número</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-167">documento numero</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-167">documento numero</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-168">registro nacional de las personas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-168">registro nacional de las personas</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-169">rnp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-169">rnp</span></span>

## <a name="argentina-unique-tax-identification-key-cuitcuil"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-170">アルゼンチン固有の税識別キー (CUIT/CUIL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-170">Argentina Unique Tax Identification Key (CUIT/CUIL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-171">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-171">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-172">ダッシュ付き 11 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-172">11 digits with dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-173">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-173">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-174">ダッシュ付き 11 桁:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-174">11 digits with a dash:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-175">20、23、24、27、30、33、34 の 2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-175">two digits in 20, 23, 24, 27, 30, 33 or 34</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-176">ハイフン (-)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-176">a hyphen (-)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-177">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-177">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-178">ハイフン (-)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-178">a hyphen (-)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-179">1 つのチェックディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-179">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-180">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-180">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-181">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-181">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-182">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-182">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-183">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-183">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-184">この関数 `Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-184">The function `Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-185">キーワードが `Keyword_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-185">A keyword from `Keyword_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-186">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-186">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-187">この関数 `Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-187">The function `Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Argentina Unique Tax Identification Key (CUIT/CUIL) -->
      <Entity id="98da3da1-9199-4571-b7c4-b6522980b507" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-193">Clave Única de Identificación Tributaria</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-193">Clave Única de Identificación Tributaria</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-194">一意の労働識別コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-194">unique labour identification code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-195">CUIL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-195">CUIL</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-197">一意の労働識別キー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-197">Unique Labour Identification Key</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-198">労働識別の一意のキー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-198">Unique Key of Labour Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-199">一意の作業識別コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-199">Unique Work Identification Code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-200">一意の作業コードの識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-200">Unique Code of Work Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-201">一意の作業識別キー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-201">Unique Work Identification Key</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-202">作業識別の一意のキー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-202">Unique Key of Work Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-203">一意の税の識別コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-203">Unique Code of Tax Identification</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-205">一意の労働識別コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-205">Unique Labor Identification Code</span></span>

## <a name="australia-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-226">オーストラリアの銀行口座番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-226">Australia bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-227">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-227">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-228">銀行の状態分岐番号の付きまたは指定なしの 6 ~ 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-228">six to 10 digits with or without a bank state branch number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-229">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-229">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-230">アカウント番号は 6 ~ 10 桁です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-230">Account number is 6 to 10 digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-231">オーストラリアの銀行の州支店番号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-231">Australia bank state branch number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-232">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-232">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-233">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-233">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-234">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-234">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-235">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-235">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-236">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-236">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-237">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-237">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-238">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-238">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-239">正規表現は、Regex_australia_bank_account_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-239">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-240">Keyword_australia_bank_account_number のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-240">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-241">正規表現 Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-241">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-242">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-242">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-243">正規表現は、Regex_australia_bank_account_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-243">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-244">Keyword_australia_bank_account_number のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-244">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="74a54de9-2a30-4aa0-a8aa-3d9327fc07c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb" />
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
  </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-252">bank address</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-252">bank address</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-258">full names</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-258">full names</span></span>

## <a name="australia-business-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-260">オーストラリアのビジネス番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-260">Australia business number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-261">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-261">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-262">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-262">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-263">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-263">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-264">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-264">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-265">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-265">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-266">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-266">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-267">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-267">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-268">11 桁の数字 (オプションの区切り記号付き)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-268">11 digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-269">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-269">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-270">11 桁の数字とオプションの区切り記号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-270">11 digits with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-271">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-271">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-272">オプションのハイフンまたはスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-272">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-273">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-273">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-274">オプションのハイフンまたはスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-274">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-275">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-275">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-276">オプションのハイフンまたはスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-276">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-277">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-277">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-278">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-278">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-279">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-279">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-280">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-280">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-281">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-281">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-282">この関数はFunc_australian_business_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-282">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-283">このページのKeywords_australian_business_numberが見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-283">A keyword from Keywords_australian_business_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-284">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-284">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-285">この関数はFunc_australian_business_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-285">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Business Number -->
      <Entity id="76e83b3b-01ee-4530-aced-e667a6609f49" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-286">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-286">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-292">ビジネス ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-292">business id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-293">abn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-293">abn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-294">businessno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-294">businessno#</span></span>

## <a name="australia-company-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-295">オーストラリアの会社番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-295">Australia company number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-296">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-296">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-297">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-297">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-298">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-298">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-299">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-299">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-300">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-300">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-301">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-301">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-302">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-302">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-303">区切り記号付き 9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-303">nine digits with delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-304">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-304">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-305">区切り記号が付く 9 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-305">nine digits with delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-306">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-306">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-307">スペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-307">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-308">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-308">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-309">スペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-309">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-310">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-310">three digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-311">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-311">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-312">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-312">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-313">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-313">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-314">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-314">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-315">この関数はFunc_Australian_Company_Number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-315">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-316">このページのKeyword_Australian_Company_Numberが見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-316">A keyword from Keyword_Australian_Company_Number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-317">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-317">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-318">この関数はFunc_Australian_Company_Number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-318">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Company Number -->
      <Entity id="b1fba4f7-7b3e-4bb9-8f9a-9366df604dbb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-328">オーストラリアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-328">Australia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-329">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-329">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-330">9 文字と数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-330">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-331">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-331">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-332">9 文字と数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-332">nine letters and digits:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-333">2 桁の数字または文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-333">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-334">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-334">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-335">5 桁または 1 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-335">five digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-336">または</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-336">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-337">1 ~ 2 文字の省略可能な文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-337">one to two optional letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-338">4 ~ 9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-338">four to nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-339">または</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-339">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-340">9 桁の数字または文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-340">nine digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-341">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-341">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-342">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-342">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-343">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-343">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-344">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-344">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-345">正規表現 Regex_australia_drivers_license_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-345">The regular expression Regex_australia_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-346">Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-346">A keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-347">Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions のキーワードを検出しなかった。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-347">No keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Drivers License Number -->
<Entity id="1cbbc8f5-9216-4392-9eb5-5ac2298d1356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-medical-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-447">オーストラリアの医療アカウント番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-447">Australia medical account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-448">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-448">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-449">10 ～ 11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-449">10-11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-450">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-450">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-451">10 ～ 11 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-451">10-11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-452">最初の桁は 2 ～ 6 のいずれか</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-452">First digit is in the range 2-6</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-453">9 桁目はチェック ディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-453">Ninth digit is a check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-454">10 桁目は発行桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-454">Tenth digit is the issue digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-455">11 桁目 (省略可能) は個人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-455">Eleventh digit (optional) is the individual number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-456">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-456">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-457">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-457">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-458">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-458">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-459">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-459">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-460">関数 Func_australian_medical_account_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-460">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-461">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-461">A keyword from Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-462">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-462">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
  <!-- Australia Medical Account Number -->
<Entity id="104a99a0-3d3b-4542-a40d-ab0b9e1efe63" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-463">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-463">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_medical_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-464">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-464">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-465">bank account details</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-465">bank account details</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-466">medicare payments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-466">medicare payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-467">mortgage account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-467">mortgage account</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-468">bank payments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-468">bank payments</span></span>

## <a name="australia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-474">オーストラリアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-474">Australia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-475">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-475">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-476">8 文字または 9 文字の英数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-476">eight or nine alphanumeric characters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-477">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-477">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-478">1 文字 (N、E、D、F、A、C、U、X) の後に 7 桁の数字または</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-478">one letter (N, E, D, F, A, C, U, X) followed by seven digits or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-479">2 文字 (PA、PB、PC、PD、PE、PF、PU、PW、PX、PZ) の後に 7 桁の数字が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-479">Two letters (PA, PB, PC, PD, PE, PF, PU, PW, PX, PZ) followed by seven digits.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-480">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-480">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-481">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-481">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-482">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-482">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-483">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-483">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-484">正規表現は、 `Regex_australia_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-484">The regular expression `Regex_australia_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-485">キーワードが `Keyword_australia_passport_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-485">A keyword from `Keyword_australia_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-486">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-486">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-487">正規表現は、 `Regex_australia_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-487">The regular expression `Regex_australia_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Australia Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="29869db6-602d-4853-ab93-3484f905df50" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-tax-file-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-507">オーストラリアの税ファイル番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-507">Australia tax file number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-508">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-508">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-509">8 桁から 9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-509">eight to nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-510">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-510">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-511">通常、8 ~ 9 桁の数字には、次のようにスペースが表示されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-511">eight to nine digits typically presented with spaces as follows:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-512">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-512">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-513">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-513">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-514">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-514">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-515">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-515">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-516">最後の数字がチェック桁である 2 ~ 3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-516">two to three digits where the last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-517">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-517">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-518">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-518">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-519">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-519">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-520">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-520">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-521">関数 Func_australian_tax_file_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-521">The function Func_australian_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-522">Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number または Keyword_number_exclusions のキーワードを検出しなかった。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-522">No keyword from Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number or Keyword_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-523">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-523">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
   <!-- Australia Tax File Number -->
    <Entity id="e29bc95f-ff70-4a37-aa01-04d17360a4c5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_tax_file_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-524">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-524">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-525">Keyword_australia_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-525">Keyword_australia_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-528">medicare levy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-528">medicare levy</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-529">portfolio number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-529">portfolio number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-532">individual tax return</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-532">individual tax return</span></span>

## <a name="austria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-535">オーストリアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-535">Austria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-536">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-536">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-537">スペースと区切り記号のない 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-537">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-538">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-538">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-539">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-539">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-540">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-540">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-541">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-541">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-542">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-542">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-543">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-543">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-544">正規表現は、  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-544">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-545">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-545">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="682f18ce-44eb-482b-8198-2bcb96a0761e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-670">Führerscheinnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-670">Führerscheinnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-671">Führerscheinnummern</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-671">Führerscheinnummern</span></span>

## <a name="austria-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-672">オーストリアの ID カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-672">Austria identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-673">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-673">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-674">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-674">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-675">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-675">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-676">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-676">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-677">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-677">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-678">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-678">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-679">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-679">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-680">文字、数字、特殊文字の 24 文字の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-680">A 24-character combination of letters, digits, and special characters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-681">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-681">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-682">24 文字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-682">24 characters:</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-683">22 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)、数字、円記号、スラッシュ、またはプラス記号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-683">22 letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, or plus signs</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-684">2 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)、数字、円記号、スラッシュ、プラス記号、または等号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-684">two letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, plus signs, or equal signs</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-685">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-685">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-686">該当しない</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-686">Not applicable</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-687">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-687">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-688">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-688">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-689">正規表現は、  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-689">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-690">キーワードが  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-690">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="5ec06c3b-007e-4820-8343-7ff73b889735" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-691">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-691">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-692">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-692">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-693">ID 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-693">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-694">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-694">national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-695">personalausweis republik österreich</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-695">personalausweis republik österreich</span></span>

## <a name="austria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-696">オーストリアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-696">Austria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-697">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-697">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-698">1 文字の後にオプションのスペースと 7 桁の数字が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-698">One letter followed by an optional space and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-699">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-699">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-700">1 文字、7 桁、および 1 つのスペースの組み合わせ。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-700">A combination of one letter, seven digits, and one space:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-701">1 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-701">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-702">1 つのスペース (オプション)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-702">one space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-703">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-703">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-704">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-704">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-705">該当なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-705">not applicable</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-706">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-706">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-707">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-707">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-708">正規表現は、  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-708">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-709">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-709">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-710">正規表現が `Regex_eu_passport_date1` DD.MM.YYYYY 形式の日付を検索するか、キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-710">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-711">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-711">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-712">正規表現は、  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-712">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-713">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-713">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1c96ae4e-303b-447d-86c7-77113ac266bf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-715">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-715">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-719">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-719">passports</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-723">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-723">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-724">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-724">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-725">パスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-725">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-726">Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-726">Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-727">reisepassnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-727">reisepassnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-728">reisepasse</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-728">reisepasse</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-729">No-Reisepass</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-729">No-Reisepass</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-730">Nr-Reisepass</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-730">Nr-Reisepass</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-731">Reisepass-Nr</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-731">Reisepass-Nr</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-732">Passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-732">Passnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-733">reisepässe</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-733">reisepässe</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_date"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-734">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-734">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-735">発行日</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-735">date of issue</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-736">有効期限の日付</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-736">date of expiry</span></span>

## <a name="austria-social-security-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-737">オーストリアの社会保障番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-737">Austria social security number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-738">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-738">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-739">指定した形式の 10 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-739">10 digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-740">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-740">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-741">10 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-741">10 digits:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-742">シリアル番号に対応する 3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-742">three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-743">1 つのチェックディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-743">one check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-744">生年月日に対応する 6 桁の数字 (DDMMYY)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-744">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-745">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-745">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-746">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-746">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-747">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-747">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-748">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-748">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-749">この関数  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-749">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-750">キーワードが  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-750">a keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-751">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-751">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-752">この関数  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-752">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Social Security Number -->
      <Entity id="6896a906-86c9-4d19-a2da-6e43ccd19b7b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-753">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-753">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-754">Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-754">Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-755">オーストリアの ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-755">austrian ssn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-756">ehic 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-756">ehic number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-757">ehic no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-757">ehic no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-758">保険コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-758">insurance code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-759">insurancecode#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-759">insurancecode#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-760">保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-760">insurance number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-761">保険なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-761">insurance no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-762">krankenkassennummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-762">krankenkassennummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-763">krankenversicherung</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-763">krankenversicherung</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-764">socialsecurityno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-764">socialsecurityno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-765">socialsecurityno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-765">socialsecurityno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-766">社会保障なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-766">social security no</span></span>

## <a name="austria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-778">オーストリアの納税者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-778">Austria tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-779">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-779">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-780">オプションのハイフンとスラッシュを含む 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-780">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-781">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-781">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-782">オプションのハイフンとスラッシュを含む 9 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-782">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-783">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-783">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-784">ハイフン (オプション)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-784">a hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-785">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-785">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-786">スラッシュ (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-786">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-787">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-787">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-788">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-788">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-789">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-789">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-790">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-790">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-791">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-791">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-792">この関数  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-792">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-793">キーワードが  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-793">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-794">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-794">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-795">この関数  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-795">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="4fd58d22-af28-4451-b18a-6f722430a56d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-value-added-tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-818">オーストリアの付加価値税</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-818">Austria value added tax</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-819">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-819">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-820">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-820">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-821">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-821">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-822">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-822">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-823">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-823">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-824">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-824">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-825">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-825">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-826">11 文字の英数字パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-826">11-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-827">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-827">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-828">11 文字の英数字パターン:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-828">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-829">A または a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-829">A or a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-830">T または t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-830">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-831">オプションの領域</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-831">Optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-832">U または u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-832">U or u</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-833">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-833">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-834">2 桁または 3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-834">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-835">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-835">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-836">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-836">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-837">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-837">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-838">1 桁または 2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-838">one or two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-839">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-839">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-840">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-840">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-841">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-841">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-842">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-842">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-843">この関数はFunc_Austria_Value_Added_Tax一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-843">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-844">ユーザーからのキーワードKeyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-844">A keyword from Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-845">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-845">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-846">この関数はFunc_Austria_Value_Added_Tax一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-846">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="b6a3eda2-c56c-4b69-a5f7-dca34db00f48" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-851">オーストリアの vat 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-851">austrian vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-852">vat No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-852">vat no.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-855">オーストリアの vat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-855">austrian vat</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-856">mwst</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-856">mwst</span></span>

## <a name="azure-documentdb-auth-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-864">Azure DocumentDB 認証キー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-864">Azure DocumentDB auth key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-865">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-865">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-866">文字列 "DocumentDb" の後に、次のパターンで概説されている文字と文字列が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-866">The string "DocumentDb" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-867">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-867">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-868">文字列 "DocumentDb"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-868">The string "DocumentDb"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-869">3 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-869">Any combination of between 3-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-870">大きい記号 (>)、等号 (=)、二重引用符 (")、またはアポストロフィ (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-870">A greater than symbol (>), an equal sign (=), a quotation mark ("), or an apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-871">86 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、スラッシュ (/)、またはプラス記号 (+) の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-871">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-872">2 つの等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-872">Two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-873">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-873">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-874">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-874">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-875">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-875">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-876">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-876">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-877">正規表現は、CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-877">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-878">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywords一致するコンテンツが見当たらない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-878">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Azure Document DB Auth Key -->
<Entity id="0f587d92-eb28-44a9-bd1c-90f2892b47aa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
          </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-885">サンドボックス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-885">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-886">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-886">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-887">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-887">localhost</span></span>
