## <a name="azure-iaas-database-connection-string-and-azure-sql-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-893">Azure IAAS データベース接続文字列と Azure SQL接続文字列</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-893">Azure IAAS database connection string and Azure SQL connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-894">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-894">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-895">文字列 "Server"、"server"、または "data source" の後に、以下のパターンで概説されている文字列 ("cloudapp.azure" という文字列を含む) が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-895">The string "Server", "server", or "data source" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-896">com" または "cloudapp.azure" を指定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-896">com" or "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-897">net" または "database.windows" を指定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-897">net" or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-898">net"、および文字列 "Password" または "password" または "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-898">net", and the string "Password" or "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-899">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-899">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-900">文字列 "Server"、"server"、または "data source"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-900">the string "Server", "server", or "data source"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-901">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-901">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-902">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-902">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-903">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-903">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-904">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-904">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-905">"cloudapp.azure" という文字列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-905">The string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-906">com", "cloudapp.azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-906">com", "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-907">net"、または "database.windows" を指定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-907">net", or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-908">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-908">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-909">1 ~ 300 の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-909">any combination of between 1-300 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-910">文字列 "Password"、"password"、または "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-910">the string "Password", "password", or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-911">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-911">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-912">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-912">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-913">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-913">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-914">セミコロンでない 1 つ以上の文字 (;)、引用符 (")、またはアポストロフィ (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-914">one or more characters that aren't a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-915">セミコロン (;)、引用符 (")、またはアポストロフィ (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-915">a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-916">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-916">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-917">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-917">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-918">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-918">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-919">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-919">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-920">正規表現は、CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-920">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-921">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywords一致するコンテンツが見当たらない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-921">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IAAS Database Connection String and Azure SQL Connection String-->
<Entity id="ce1a126d-186f-4700-8c0c-486157b953fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-929">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-929">onebox</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-931">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-931">127.0.0.1</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-934">s-int。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-934">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-935">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-935">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-iot-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-936">Azure IoT接続文字列</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-936">Azure IoT connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-937">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-937">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-938">文字列 "HostName" の後に、以下のパターンで概説されている文字列 ("azure-devices" という文字列を含む) が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-938">The string "HostName" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-939">net」と「SharedAccessKey」。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-939">net" and "SharedAccessKey".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-942">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-942">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-943">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-943">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-944">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-944">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-945">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-945">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-946">文字列 "azure-devices.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-946">the string "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-947">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-947">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-948">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-948">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-949">文字列 "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-949">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-950">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-950">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-951">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-951">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-952">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-952">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-953">43 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、スラッシュ (/)、またはプラス記号 (+) の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-953">any combination of 43 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-954">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-954">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-955">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-955">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-956">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-956">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-957">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-957">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-958">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-958">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-960">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywords一致するコンテンツが見当たらない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-960">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


## <a name="azure-publish-setting-password"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-975">Azure 発行設定パスワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-975">Azure publish setting password</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-976">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-976">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-977">文字列 "userpwd=" の後に英数字の文字列が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-977">The string "userpwd=" followed by an alphanumeric string.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-978">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-978">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-979">文字列 "userpwd="</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-979">the string "userpwd="</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-980">60 文字の小文字または数字の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-980">any combination of 60 lowercase letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-981">引用符 (")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-981">a quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-982">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-982">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-983">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-983">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-984">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-984">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-985">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-985">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-986">正規表現は、CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-986">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-987">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywords一致するコンテンツが見当たらない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-987">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
<!--Azure Publish Setting Password-->
<Entity id="75f4cc8a-a68e-49e5-89ce-fa8f03d286a5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
       <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords" />
       <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
           <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
       </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-988">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-988">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_common_example_keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-989">CEP_common_example_keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-989">CEP_common_example_keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-990">(技術的には、この機密情報の種類は、キーワード リストではなく正規表現を使用してこれらのキーワードを識別します)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-990">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-991">contoso</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-991">contoso</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-992">fabrikam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-992">fabrikam</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-993">northwind</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-993">northwind</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-994">サンドボックス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-994">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-995">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-995">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-996">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-996">localhost</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-997">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-997">127.0.0.1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-998">testacs。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-998">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-999">com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-999">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1000">s-int。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1000">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1001">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1001">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-redis-cache-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1002">Azure Redis キャッシュ接続文字列</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1002">Azure Redis cache connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1003">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1003">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1004">文字列 "redis.cache.windows。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1004">The string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1005">net" の後に、文字列 "password" または "pwd" を含む、以下のパターンで概説されている文字と文字列が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1005">net" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1006">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1006">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1007">文字列 "redis.cache.windows" を指定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1007">the string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1008">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1008">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1009">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1009">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1010">文字列 "password" または "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1010">the string "password" or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1011">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1011">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1012">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1012">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1013">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1013">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1014">小文字または大文字、数字、スラッシュ (/)、またはプラス記号 (+) の 43 文字の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1014">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1015">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1015">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1016">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1016">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1017">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1017">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1018">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1018">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1019">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1019">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1020">正規表現は、CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1020">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1021">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywords一致するコンテンツが見当たらない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1021">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Redis Cache Connection String-->
<Entity id="095a7e6c-efd8-46d5-af7b-5298d53a49fc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1022">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1022">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_common_example_keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1023">CEP_common_example_keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1023">CEP_common_example_keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1024">(技術的には、この機密情報の種類は、キーワード リストではなく正規表現を使用してこれらのキーワードを識別します)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1024">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1025">contoso</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1025">contoso</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1026">fabrikam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1026">fabrikam</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1027">northwind</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1027">northwind</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1028">サンドボックス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1028">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1029">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1029">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1030">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1030">localhost</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1031">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1031">127.0.0.1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1032">testacs。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1032">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1033">com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1033">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1034">s-int。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1034">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1035">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1035">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-sas"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1036">Azure SAS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1036">Azure SAS</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1037">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1037">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1038">文字列 "sig" の後に、以下のパターンで概説されている文字と文字列が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1038">The string "sig" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1039">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1039">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1040">文字列 "sig"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1040">the string "sig"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1041">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1041">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1042">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1042">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1043">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1043">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1044">小文字または大文字、数字、またはパーセント記号 (%) である 43 ~ 53 文字の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1044">any combination of between 43-53 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, or the percent sign (%)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1045">文字列 "%3d"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1045">the string "%3d"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1046">小文字または大文字、数字、またはパーセント記号 (%) ではない文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1046">any character that isn't a lower- or uppercase letter, digit, or percent sign (%)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1047">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1047">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1048">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1048">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1049">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1049">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1050">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1050">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1051">正規表現は、CEP_Regex_AzureSAS一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1051">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureSAS finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure SAS-->
<Entity id="4d235014-e564-47f4-a6fb-6ebb4a826834" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureSAS" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-service-bus-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1052">Azure Service バス接続文字列</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1052">Azure service bus connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1053">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1053">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1054">文字列 "EndPoint" の後に、文字列 "servicebus.windows" を含む、以下のパターンで概説されている文字と文字列が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1054">The string "EndPoint" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1055">net」および「SharedAccesKey」を参照してください。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1055">net" and "SharedAccesKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1056">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1056">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1057">文字列 "EndPoint"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1057">the string "EndPoint"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1058">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1058">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1059">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1059">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1060">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1060">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1061">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1061">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1062">文字列 "servicebus.windows" を指定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1062">the string "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1063">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1063">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1064">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1064">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1065">文字列 "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1065">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1066">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1066">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1067">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1067">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1068">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1068">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1069">小文字または大文字、数字、スラッシュ (/)、またはプラス記号 (+) の 43 文字の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1069">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1070">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1070">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1071">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1071">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1072">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1072">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1073">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1073">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1074">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1074">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1075">正規表現は、CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1075">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1076">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywords一致するコンテンツが見当たらない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1076">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Service Bus Connection String-->
<Entity id="b9a6578f-a83f-4fcd-bf44-2130bae49a6f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1091">Azure ストレージ アカウント キー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1091">Azure storage account key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1092">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1092">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1093">"DefaultEndpointsProtocol" という文字列の後に、"AccountKey" という文字列を含む、以下のパターンで概説されている文字と文字列が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1093">The string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "AccountKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1094">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1094">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1095">文字列 "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1095">the string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1096">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1096">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1097">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1097">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1098">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1098">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1099">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1099">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1100">文字列 "AccountKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1100">the string "AccountKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1101">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1101">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1102">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1102">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1103">0 から 2 文字の空白文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1103">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1104">小文字または大文字、数字、スラッシュ (/)、またはプラス記号 (+) である 86 文字の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1104">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1105">2 つの等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1105">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1106">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1106">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1107">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1107">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1108">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1108">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1109">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1109">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1110">正規表現は、CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1110">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1111">パターンに一CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter一致するコンテンツが見当たらない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1111">The regular expression CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1112">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywords一致するコンテンツが見当たらない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1112">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key-->
<Entity id="c7bc98e8-551a-4c35-a92d-d2c8cda714a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1118">(技術的には、この機密情報の種類は、キーワード リストではなく正規表現を使用してこれらのキーワードを識別します)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1118">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key-generic"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1130">Azure Storage アカウント キー (汎用)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1130">Azure Storage account key (generic)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1131">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1131">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1132">86 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、スラッシュ (/)、またはプラス記号 (+) の任意の組み合わせで、次のパターンで説明されている文字が先行または続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1132">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+), preceded or followed by the characters outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1133">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1133">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1134">0 から 1 の大きい記号 (>)、アポストロフィ (')、等号 (=)、二重引用符 (")、または番号記号 (#)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1134">zero to one of the greater than symbol (>), apostrophe ('), equal sign (=), quotation mark ("), or number sign (#)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1135">小文字または大文字、数字、スラッシュ (/)、またはプラス記号 (+) である 86 文字の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1135">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1136">2 つの等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1136">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1137">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1137">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1138">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1138">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1139">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1139">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1140">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1140">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1141">正規表現は、CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1141">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key (Generic)-->
<Entity id="7ff41bd0-5419-4523-91d6-383b3a37f084" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
## <a name="belgium-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1142">ベルギーの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1142">Belgium driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1143">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1143">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1144">スペースと区切り記号のない 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1144">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1145">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1145">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1146">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1146">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1147">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1147">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1148">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1148">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1149">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1149">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1150">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1150">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1151">正規表現は、  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1151">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1152">キーワードが見 `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1152">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d89fd329-9324-433c-b687-2c37bd5166f3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-national-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1285">ベルギーの国番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1285">Belgium national number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1286">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1286">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1287">11 桁の数字とオプションの区切り記号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1287">11 digits plus optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1288">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1288">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1289">11 の数字と区切り文字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1289">11 digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1290">6 桁の数字と 2 つのオプションのピリオドを YY 形式で指定します。MM.DD の生年月日</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1290">six digits and two optional periods in the format YY.MM.DD for date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1291">ドット、ダッシュ、スペースからのオプションの区切り文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1291">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1292">3 桁の連続した数字 (男性の場合は奇数、女性の場合も)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1292">three sequential digits (odd for males, even for females)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1293">ドット、ダッシュ、スペースからのオプションの区切り文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1293">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1294">2 つのチェックの数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1294">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1295">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1295">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1296">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1296">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1297">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1297">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1298">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1298">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1299">この関数はFunc_belgium_national_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1299">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1300">このページのKeyword_belgium_national_number見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1300">A keyword from Keyword_belgium_national_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1301">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1301">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1302">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1302">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1303">この関数はFunc_belgium_national_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1303">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1304">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1304">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Belgium National Number -->
       <Entity id="fb969c9e-0fd1-4b18-8091-a2123c5e6a54" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1363">ベルギーのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1363">Belgium passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1364">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1364">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1365">2 文字の後に 6 桁の数字が続き、スペースまたは区切り記号は使用されません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1365">two letters followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1366">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1366">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1367">2 文字、その後に 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1367">two letters and followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1368">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1368">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1369">該当なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1369">not applicable</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1370">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1370">Definition</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1371">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1371">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1372">正規表現は、  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1372">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1373">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1373">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1374">正規表現は、DD MM YY 形式の日付を検索するか、検索 `Regex_eu_passport_date2` されたキーワード `Keywords_eu_passport_date` を `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` 検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1374">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1375">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1375">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1376">正規表現は、  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1376">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1377">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1377">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d7b1315b-21ca-4774-a32a-596010ff78fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="belgium-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1404">ベルギーの付加価値税番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1404">Belgium value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1405">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1405">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1406">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1406">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1407">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1407">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1408">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1408">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1409">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1409">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1410">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1410">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1411">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1411">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1412">12 文字の英数字パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1412">12-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1413">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1413">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1414">12 文字の英数字パターン:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1414">12-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1415">文字 B または b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1415">a letter B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1416">E または e の文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1416">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1417">数字 0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1417">a digit 0</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1418">1 ~ 9 の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1418">a digit from 1 to 9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1419">オプションのドットまたはハイフンまたはスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1419">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1420">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1420">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1421">オプションのドットまたはハイフンまたはスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1421">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1422">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1422">four digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1423">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1423">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1424">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1424">Yes</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1425">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1425">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1426">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1426">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1427">この関数はFunc_belgium_value_added_tax_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1427">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1428">ユーザーのキーワードKeywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1428">A keyword from Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1429">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1429">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1430">この関数はFunc_belgium_value_added_tax_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1430">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="85b5b3c3-f2de-4ae8-ac46-fd3cb38bf9ed" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1431">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1431">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1432">Keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1432">Keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1433">nº tva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1433">nº tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1434">vat 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1434">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1435">vat いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1435">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1436">numéro t.v.a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1436">numéro t.v.a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1437">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1437">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1438">umsatzsteuernummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1438">umsatzsteuernummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1439">btw</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1439">btw</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1440">btw#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1440">btw#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1441">vat#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1441">vat#</span></span>


## <a name="brazil-cpf-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1442">ブラジルの CPF 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1442">Brazil CPF number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1443">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1443">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1444">書式設定ありまたは書式設定なしのチェック ディジットを含む 11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1444">11 digits that include a check digit and can be formatted or unformatted</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1445">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1445">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1446">書式設定:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1446">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1447">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1447">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1448">ピリオド</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1448">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1449">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1449">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1450">ピリオド</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1450">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1451">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1451">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1452">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1452">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1453">チェックの数字である 2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1453">two digits that are check digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1454">Unformatted:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1454">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1455">11 桁の数字 (最後の 2 桁はチェック ディジット)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1455">11 digits where the last two digits are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1456">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1456">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1457">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1457">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1458">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1458">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1459">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1459">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1460">この関数はFunc_brazil_cpf一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1460">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1461">ユーザーからのキーワードKeyword_brazil_cpf見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1461">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cpf is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1462">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1462">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1463">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1463">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1464">この関数はFunc_brazil_cpf一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1464">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1465">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1465">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil CPF Number -->
<Entity id="78e09124-f2c3-4656-b32a-c1a132cd2711" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1466">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1466">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_cpf"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1467">Keyword_brazil_cpf</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1467">Keyword_brazil_cpf</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1468">CPF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1468">CPF</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1471">収益</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1471">Revenue</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1472">Cadastro de Pessoas Físicas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1472">Cadastro de Pessoas Físicas</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1473">Imposto</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1473">Imposto</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1474">Identificação</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1474">Identificação</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1475">Inscrição</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1475">Inscrição</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1476">Receita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1476">Receita</span></span>


## <a name="brazil-legal-entity-number-cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1477">ブラジルの法人番号 (CNPJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1477">Brazil legal entity number (CNPJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1478">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1478">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1479">登録番号、枝番号、チェック ディジット、および区切り文字を含む 14 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1479">14 digits that include a registration number, branch number, and check digits, plus delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1480">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1480">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1481">14 桁の数字と区切り文字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1481">14 digits, plus delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1482">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1482">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1483">ピリオド</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1483">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1484">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1484">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1485">ピリオド</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1485">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1486">3 桁 (最初の 8 桁は登録番号です)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1486">three digits (these first eight digits are the registration number)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1487">スラッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1487">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1488">4 桁の分岐番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1488">four-digit branch number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1489">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1489">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1490">チェックの数字である 2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1490">two digits that are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1491">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1491">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1492">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1492">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1493">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1493">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1494">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1494">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1495">この関数はFunc_brazil_cnpj一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1495">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1496">ユーザーからのキーワードKeyword_brazil_cnpj見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1496">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cnpj is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1497">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1497">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1498">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1498">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1499">この関数はFunc_brazil_cnpj一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1499">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1500">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1500">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil Legal Entity Number (CNPJ) -->
<Entity id="9b58b5cd-5e90-4df6-b34f-1ebcc88ceae4" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1501">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1501">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1502">Keyword_brazil_cnpj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1502">Keyword_brazil_cnpj</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1503">CNPJ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1503">CNPJ</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1504">CNPJ/MF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1504">CNPJ/MF</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1505">CNPJ-MF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1505">CNPJ-MF</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1506">National Registry of Legal Entities</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1506">National Registry of Legal Entities</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1507">Taxpayers Registry</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1507">Taxpayers Registry</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1508">Legal entity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1508">Legal entity</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1509">Legal entities</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1509">Legal entities</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1510">Registration Status</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1510">Registration Status</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1511">Business</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1511">Business</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1512">会社名</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1512">Company</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1513">CNPJ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1513">CNPJ</span></span>

## <a name="brazil-national-identification-card-rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1522">ブラジルの国民識別カード (RG)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1522">Brazil national identification card (RG)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1523">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1523">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1524">Registro Geral (旧形式): 9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1524">Registro Geral (old format): Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1525">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (新しい形式): 11 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1525">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format): 11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1526">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1526">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1527">Registro Geral (従来の形式):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1527">Registro Geral (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1528">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1528">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1529">ピリオド</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1529">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1530">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1530">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1531">ピリオド</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1531">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1532">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1532">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1533">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1533">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1534">チェックディジットである 1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1534">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1535">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (新しい形式):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1535">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1536">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1536">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1537">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1537">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1538">チェックディジットである 1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1538">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1539">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1539">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1540">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1540">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1541">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1541">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1542">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1542">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1543">この関数はFunc_brazil_rg一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1543">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1544">ユーザーからのキーワードKeyword_brazil_rg見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1544">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_rg is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1545">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1545">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- Brazil National ID Card (RG) -->
      <Entity id="486de900-db70-41b3-a886-abdf25af119c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_rg" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1546">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1546">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1547">Keyword_brazil_rg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1547">Keyword_brazil_rg</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1548">Cédula de identidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1548">Cédula de identidade</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1549">Identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1549">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1550">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1550">national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1551">número de rregistro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1551">número de rregistro</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1552">registro de Iidentidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1552">registro de Iidentidade</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1553">registro geral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1553">registro geral</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1554">RG (このキーワードでは大文字と小文字が区別されます)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1554">RG (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1555">RIC (このキーワードでは大文字と小文字が区別されます)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1555">RIC (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span>


## <a name="bulgaria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1556">ブルガリアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1556">Bulgaria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1557">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1557">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1558">スペースと区切り記号のない 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1558">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1559">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1559">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1560">9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1560">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1561">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1561">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1562">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1562">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1563">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1563">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1564">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1564">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1565">正規表現は、  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1565">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-1566">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-1566">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="66d39258-94c2-43b2-804b-aa312258e54b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
