## <a name="czech-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3163">チェコのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3163">Czech passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3164">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3164">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3165">スペースまたは区切り記号のない 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3165">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3166">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3166">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3167">スペースまたは区切り記号のない 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3167">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3168">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3168">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3169">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3169">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3170">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3170">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3171">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3171">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3172">正規表現は、  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3172">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3173">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3173">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3174">正規表現が `Regex_eu_passport_date1` DD.MM.YYYYY 形式の日付を検索するか、キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3174">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3175">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3175">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3176">正規表現は、  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3176">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3177">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3177">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Czech Republic Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7bcd8ce8-5e92-4bbe-bc92-fa669f0369fa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-personal-identity-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3199">チェコの個人 ID 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3199">Czech personal identity number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3200">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3200">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3201">オプションのスラッシュ付き 9 桁 (古い形式) 10 桁 、オプションのスラッシュ (新しい形式)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3201">nine digits with optional forward slash (old format) 10 digits with optional forward slash (new format)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3202">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3202">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3203">9 桁 (古い形式):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3203">nine digits (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3204">生年月日を表す 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3204">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3205">オプションのスラッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3205">an optional forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3206">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3206">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3207">10 桁 (新しい形式):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3207">10 digits (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3208">生年月日を表す 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3208">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3209">オプションのスラッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3209">an optional forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3210">最後の数字がチェック桁である 4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3210">four digits where last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3211">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3211">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3212">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3212">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3213">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3213">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3214">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3214">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3215">この関数はFunc_czech_id_card一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3215">The function Func_czech_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3216">ユーザーからのキーワードKeyword_czech_id_card見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3216">A keyword from Keyword_czech_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3217">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3217">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3218">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3218">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3219">この関数Func_czech_id_card_new_format一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3219">The function Func_czech_id_card_new_format finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3220">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3220">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <Entity id="60c0725a-4eb6-455b-9dda-05d8a7396497" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_czech_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3000.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card_new_format" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3232">保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3232">insurance number</span></span>

## <a name="denmark-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3267">デンマークの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3267">Denmark driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3268">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3268">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3269">スペースと区切り記号のない 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3269">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3270">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3270">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3271">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3271">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3272">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3272">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3273">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3273">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3274">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3274">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3275">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3275">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3276">正規表現は、  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3276">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3277">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3277">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Denmark Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="98a95812-6203-451a-a220-d39870ebef0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3401">デンマークのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3401">Denmark passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3402">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3402">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3403">スペースと区切り記号のない 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3403">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3404">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3404">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3405">9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3405">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3406">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3406">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3407">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3407">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3408">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3408">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3409">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3409">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3410">正規表現は、  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3410">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3411">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3411">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3412">正規表現が DD MM YY 形式の日付を検索するか、キーワード `Regex_eu_passport_date2` が `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3412">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3413">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3413">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3414">正規表現は、  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3414">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3415">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3415">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Denmark Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="25e8c47e-e6fe-4884-a211-74898f8c0196" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="denmark-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3435">デンマークの個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3435">Denmark personal identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3436">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3436">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3437">ハイフンを 1 つ含む 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3437">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3438">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3438">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3439">10 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3439">10 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3440">DDMMYY 形式の 6 桁の数字 (生年月日)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3440">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3441">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3441">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3442">最後の数字がチェック桁である 4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3442">four digits where the final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3443">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3443">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3444">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3444">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3445">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3445">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3446">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3446">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3447">正規表現は、Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3447">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3448">ユーザーのキーワードKeyword_denmark_id見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3448">A keyword from Keyword_denmark_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3449">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3449">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3450">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3450">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3451">正規表現は、Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3451">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3452">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3452">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
    <!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="6c4f2fef-56e1-4c00-8093-88d7a01cf460" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_denmark_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3463">健康保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3463">health insurance number</span></span>

## <a name="drug-enforcement-agency-dea-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3524">麻薬取締局 (DEA) 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3524">Drug Enforcement Agency (DEA) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3525">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3525">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3526">2 文字の後に 7 桁の数字を付け</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3526">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3527">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3527">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3528">パターンには、以下のすべてが含まれる必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3528">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3529">可能な文字のこのセットからの 1 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません): abcdefghjklmnprstux (レジストリ コード)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3529">one letter (not case-sensitive) from this set of possible letters: abcdefghjklmnprstux, which is a registrant code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3530">1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない) (登録者の名または数字 '9' の最初の文字)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3530">one letter (not case-sensitive), which is the first letter of the registrant's last name or digit '9'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3531">7 桁の数字で、最後の数字はチェック桁です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3531">seven digits, the last of which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3532">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3532">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3533">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3533">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3534">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3534">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3535">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3535">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3536">関数 Func_dea_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3536">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3537">キーワードが `Keyword_dea_number` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3537">A keyword from `Keyword_dea_number` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3538">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3538">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3539">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3539">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3540">関数 Func_dea_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3540">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3541">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3541">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- DEA Number -->
    <Entity id="9a5445ad-406e-43eb-8bd7-cac17ab6d0e4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
      </Pattern>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.1207.000" maxEngineVersion="15.20.3134.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3135.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3542">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3542">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_dea_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3543">Keyword_dea_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3543">Keyword_dea_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3544">dea</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3544">dea</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3545">dea#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3545">dea#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3546">麻薬取締局</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3546">drug enforcement administration</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3547">麻薬取締局</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3547">drug enforcement agency</span></span>


## <a name="estonia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3548">エストニアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3548">Estonia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3549">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3549">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3550">2 文字の後に 6 桁の数字が続く</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3550">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3551">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3551">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3552">2 文字と 6 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3552">two letters and six digits:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3553">文字 "ET" (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3553">the letters "ET" (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3554">6 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3554">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3555">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3555">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3556">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3556">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3557">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3557">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3558">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3558">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3559">正規表現は、  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3559">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3560">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3560">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Estonia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="51da8171-da70-4cc1-9d65-055a59ca4f83" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-personal-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3686">エストニアの個人識別コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3686">Estonia Personal Identification Code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3687">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3687">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3688">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3688">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3689">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3689">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3690">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3690">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3691">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3691">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3692">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3692">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3693">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3693">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3694">スペースと区切り記号のない 11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3694">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3695">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3695">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3696">11 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3696">11 digits:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3697">性別と出生世紀に対応する 1 桁の数字 (奇数男性、偶数女性、1-2:19 世紀、3-4: 20 世紀、5~6:21 世紀)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3697">one digit that corresponds to sex and century of birth (odd number male, even number female; 1-2: 19th century; 3-4: 20th century; 5-6: 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3698">生年月日 (YYMMDD) に対応する 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3698">six digits that correspond to date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3699">同じ日付に生まれた人を区切るシリアル番号に対応する 3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3699">three digits that correspond to a serial number separating persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3700">1 つのチェックディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3700">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3701">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3701">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3702">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3702">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3703">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3703">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3704">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3704">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3705">この関数  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3705">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3706">キーワードが  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3706">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3707">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3707">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3708">この関数  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3708">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Estonia Personal Identification Code -->
      <Entity id="bfb26de6-dad5-4d48-ab72-4789cdd0654c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3741">エストニアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3741">Estonia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3742">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3742">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3743">1 文字の後にスペースまたは区切り記号を付けない 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3743">one letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3744">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3744">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3745">1 文字の後に 7 桁の数字が続く</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3745">one letter followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3746">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3746">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3747">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3747">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3748">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3748">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3749">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3749">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3750">正規表現は、  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3750">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3751">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3751">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3752">正規表現が `Regex_eu_passport_date1` DD.MM.YYYYY 形式の日付を検索するか、キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3752">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3753">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3753">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3754">正規表現は、  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3754">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3755">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3755">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Estonia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61f7073a-509e-425b-a754-bc01bb5d5b8c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number_common"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3757">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3757">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3761">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3761">passports</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3769">eesti kodaniku passi number passinumbrid document number document no dokumendi nr</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3769">eesti kodaniku pass passi number passinumbrid document number document no dokumendi nr</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_date"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3770">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3770">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span></span>

## <a name="eu-debit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3773">EU のデビット カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3773">EU debit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3774">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3774">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3775">16 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3775">16 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3776">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3776">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3777">複雑で堅牢なパターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3777">Complex and robust pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3778">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3778">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3779">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3779">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3780">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3780">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3781">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3781">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3782">関数 Func_eu_debit_card がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3782">The function Func_eu_debit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3783">次の条件のうち 1 つ以上に該当する:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3783">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3784">Keyword_eu_debit_card のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3784">A keyword from Keyword_eu_debit_card is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3785">Keyword_card_terms_dict のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3785">A keyword from Keyword_card_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3786">Keyword_card_security_terms_dict のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3786">A keyword from Keyword_card_security_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3787">Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3787">A keyword from Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3788">関数 Func_expiration_date が適切な日付形式の日付を検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3788">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3789">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3789">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- EU Debit Card Number -->
    <Entity id="0e9b3178-9678-47dd-a509-37222ca96b42" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_eu_debit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_eu_debit_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_security_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3790">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3790">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_eu_debit_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3791">Keyword_eu_debit_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3791">Keyword_eu_debit_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3792">account number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3792">account number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3793">card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3793">card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3794">card no.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3794">card no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3795">security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3795">security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-3796">cc#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-3796">cc#</span></span>

## <a name="finland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4236">フィンランドの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4236">Finland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4237">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4237">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4238">ハイフンを 1 つ含む 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4238">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4239">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4239">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4240">ハイフンを含む 10 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4240">10 digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4241">6 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4241">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4242">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4242">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4243">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4243">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4244">数字または文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4244">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4245">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4245">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4246">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4246">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4247">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4247">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4248">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4248">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4249">正規表現は、  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4249">The regular expression  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4250">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4250">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="bb3b27a3-79bd-4ac4-81a7-f9fca3c7d1a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-european-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4381">フィンランド のヨーロッパの健康保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4381">Finland european health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4382">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4382">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4383">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4383">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4384">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4384">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4385">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4385">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4386">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4386">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4387">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4387">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4388">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4388">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4389">20 桁の番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4389">20-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4390">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4390">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4391">20 桁の番号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4391">20-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4392">10 桁 - 8024680246</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4392">10 digits - 8024680246</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4393">オプションのスペースまたはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4393">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4394">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4394">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4395">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4395">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4396">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4396">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4397">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4397">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4398">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4398">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4399">正規表現はRegex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4399">The regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4400">ユーザーのキーワードKeyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4400">A keyword from Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland European Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="60f75aed-81bf-4625-89b0-0846b9248ee7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4406">finska sjukförsäkringskort</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4406">finska sjukförsäkringskort</span></span>

## <a name="finland-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4418">フィンランドの国民 ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4418">Finland national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4419">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4419">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4420">6 桁の数字と、1 世紀と 3 桁の数字とチェック桁を示す文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4420">six digits plus a character indicating a century plus three digits plus a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4421">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4421">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4422">パターンには、以下のすべてが含まれる必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4422">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4423">DDMMYY という形式の 6 桁の数字 (生年月日)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4423">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are a date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4424">century マーカー ('-','+' または 'a')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4424">century marker (either '-', '+' or 'a')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4425">3 桁の個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4425">three-digit personal identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4426">チェック桁である数字または文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4426">a digit or letter (case insensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4427">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4427">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4428">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4428">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4429">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4429">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4430">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4430">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4431">パターンにFunc_finnish_national_id一致するコンテンツを検索する関数</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4431">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4432">見つかったKeyword_finnish_national_idキーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4432">a keyword from Keyword_finnish_national_id is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4433">チェックサム パス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4433">the checksum passes</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4434">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4434">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4435">パターンにFunc_finnish_national_id一致するコンテンツを検索する関数</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4435">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4436">チェックサム パス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4436">the checksum passes</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finnish National ID-->
      <Entity id="338FD995-4CB5-4F87-AD35-79BD1DD926C1" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4485">フィンランドのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4485">Finland passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4486">このエンティティは、EU Passport Number 機密情報の種類で使用できます。スタンドアロンの機密情報の種類エンティティとして使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4486">This entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4487">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4487">Format</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4488">9 つの文字と数字の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4488">combination of nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4489">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4489">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4490">9 つの文字と数字の組み合わせ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4490">combination of nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4491">2 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4491">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4492">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4492">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4493">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4493">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4494">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4494">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4495">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4495">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4496">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4496">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4497">正規表現は、 `Regex_finland_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4497">The regular expression `Regex_finland_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4498">キーワードが見 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keyword_finland_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4498">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_finland_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4499">正規表現が `Regex_eu_passport_date1` DD.MM.YYYYY 形式の日付を検索するか、キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4499">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4500">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4500">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4501">正規表現は、 `Regex_finland_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4501">The regular expression `Regex_finland_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4502">キーワードが見 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keyword_finland_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4502">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_finland_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d1685ac3-1d3a-40f8-8198-32ef5669c7a5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_finland_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4515">Keyword_finland_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4515">Keyword_finland_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4516">suomalainen passi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4516">suomalainen passi</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4517">passin numero</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4517">passin numero</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4521">passi#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4521">passi#</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_date"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4523">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4523">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4524">発行日</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4524">date of issue</span></span>

## <a name="france-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4526">フランスの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4526">France driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4527">このエンティティは、EU ドライバーのライセンス番号の機密情報の種類で使用できます。スタンドアロンの機密情報の種類エンティティとして使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4527">This entity is available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4528">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4528">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4529">12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4529">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4530">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4530">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4531">フランスの電話番号などの同様のパターンと区別するための検証付きの 12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4531">12 digits with validation to discount similar patterns such as French telephone numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4532">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4532">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4533">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4533">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4534">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4534">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4535">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4535">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4536">この関数はFunc_french_drivers_license一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4536">the function Func_french_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4537">検索されたKeyword_french_drivers_licenseが見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4537">a keyword from Keyword_french_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="18e55a36-a01b-4b0f-943d-dc10282a1824" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_french_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4658">permis de conduire</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4658">permis de conduire</span></span>

## <a name="france-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4664">フランスの健康保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4664">France health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4665">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4665">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4666">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4666">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4667">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4667">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4668">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4668">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4669">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4669">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4670">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4670">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4671">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4671">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4672">21 桁の番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4672">21-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4673">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4673">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4674">21 桁の番号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4674">21-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4675">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4675">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4676">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4676">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4677">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4677">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4678">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4678">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4679">数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4679">a digit</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4680">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4680">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4681">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4681">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4682">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4682">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4683">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4683">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4684">正規表現はRegex_France_Health_Insurance_Number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4684">the regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4685">検索されたKeyword_France_Health_Insurance_Numberが見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4685">a keyword from Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="9bc2069e-76df-4ff9-ac02-2f519469e236" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4686">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4686">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_health_insurance_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4687">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4687">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4688">保険証</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4688">insurance card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4689">デカルトバイタル</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4689">carte vitale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4690">デカルト d'assuré social</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4690">carte d'assuré social</span></span>


## <a name="france-national-id-card-cni"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4691">フランスの国民 ID カード (CNI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4691">France national id card (CNI)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4692">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4692">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4693">12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4693">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4694">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4694">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4695">12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4695">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4696">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4696">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4697">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4697">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4698">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4698">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4699">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4699">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4700">正規表現 Regex_france_cni がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4700">The regular expression Regex_france_cni finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4701">このページのKeywords_france_eu_national_id_cardが見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4701">A keyword from Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France CNI -->
    <Entity id="f741ac74-1bc0-4665-b69b-f0c7f927c0c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="65">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_france_cni" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4702">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4702">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_france_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4703">Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4703">Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4704">card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4704">card number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4706">デカルト nationale d'idenite no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4706">carte nationale d'idenite no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4707">cni#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4707">cni#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4708">cni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4708">cni</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4709">compte bancaire</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4709">compte bancaire</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4710">national identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4710">national identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4711">国の ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4711">national identity</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4712">nationalidno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4712">nationalidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4713">numéro d'assurance maladie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4713">numéro d'assurance maladie</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4714">numéro de carte vitale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4714">numéro de carte vitale</span></span>


## <a name="france-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4715">フランスのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4715">France passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4716">このエンティティは、EU パスポート番号の機密情報の種類で使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4716">This entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4717">また、スタンドアロンの機密情報の種類エンティティとして利用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4717">It's also available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4718">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4718">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4719">9 桁の数字と文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4719">nine digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4720">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4720">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4721">9 桁の数字と文字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4721">nine digits and letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4722">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4722">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4723">2 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4723">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4724">5 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4724">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4725">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4725">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4726">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4726">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4727">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4727">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4728">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4728">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4729">この関数 `Func_fr_passport` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4729">The function `Func_fr_passport` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4730">キーワードが見 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4730">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4731">正規表現が DD MM YYYY の形式で日付を検索するか、キーワード `Regex_eu_passport_date3` が `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかった</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4731">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4732">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4732">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4733">この関数 `Func_fr_passport` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4733">The function `Func_fr_passport` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4734">キーワードが見 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4734">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- France Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="3008b884-8c8c-4cd8-a289-99f34fc7ff5d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_france_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4747">Keywords_france_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4747">Keywords_france_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4748">numéro de passeport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4748">numéro de passeport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4749">passeport n °</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4749">passeport n °</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4751">passeport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4751">passeport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4752">passeport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4752">passeport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4753">passeportnon</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4753">passeportnon</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4754">passeportn °</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4754">passeportn °</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4755">passeport français</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4755">passeport français</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4756">passeport livre</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4756">passeport livre</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4757">パスポート のデカルト</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4757">passeport carte</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4758">numéro パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4758">numéro passeport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4759">passeport n°</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4759">passeport n°</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4760">n° du passeport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4760">n° du passeport</span></span>
