## <a name="france-social-security-number-insee"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4765">フランスの社会保障番号 (INSEE)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4765">France social security number (INSEE)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4766">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4766">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4767">15 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4767">15 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4768">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4768">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4769">次のいずれかのパターンに一致する:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4769">Must match one of two patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4770">13 桁の後にスペースが続き、2 桁の数字が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4770">13 digits followed by a space followed by two digits</span></span><br/>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4771">または</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4771">or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4772">15 桁の連続する数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4772">15 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4773">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4773">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4774">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4774">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4775">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4775">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4776">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4776">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4777">この関数 `Func_french_insee` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4777">The function `Func_french_insee` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4778">Keyword_fr_insee のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4778">A keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4779">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4779">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4780">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4780">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4781">この関数はFunc_french_inseeまたはFunc_fr_insee一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4781">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4782">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4782">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France INSEE -->
    <Entity id="71f62b97-efe0-4aa1-aa49-e14de253619d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

no. d'identite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-p134">no. d'identite</span></span>

## <a name="france-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4813">フランスの納税者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4813">France tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4814">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4814">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4815">13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4815">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4816">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4816">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4817">13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4817">13 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4818">0、1、2、または 3 である必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4818">One digit that must be 0, 1, 2, or 3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4819">1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4819">One digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4820">スペース 1 つ (省略可能) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4820">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4821">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4821">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4822">スペース 1 つ (省略可能) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4822">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4823">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4823">Three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4824">スペース 1 つ (省略可能) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4824">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4825">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4825">Three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4826">スペース 1 つ (省略可能) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4826">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4827">3 つのチェックの数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4827">Three check digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4828">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4828">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4829">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4829">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4830">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4830">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4831">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4831">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4832">この関数  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4832">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4833">キーワードが  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4833">A keyword from  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4834">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4834">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4835">この関数  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4835">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Tax Identification Number (numéro SPI.) -->
      <Entity id="ed59e77e-171d-442c-9ec1-88e2ebcb5b0a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4836">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4836">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4837">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4837">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4838">numéro d'id fiscale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4838">numéro d'identification fiscale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4839">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4839">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4840">税の識別なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4840">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4841">税の識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4841">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4842">tax no#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4842">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4843">tax no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4843">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4844">税番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4844">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4845">税登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4845">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4846">タクシー#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4846">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4847">taxidno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4847">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4848">taxidnumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4848">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4849">taxno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4849">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4850">taxnumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4850">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4851">taxnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4851">taxnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4852">tin id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4852">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4853">tin いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4853">tin no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4854">tin#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4854">tin#</span></span>


## <a name="france-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4855">フランスの付加価値税番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4855">France value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4856">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4856">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4857">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4857">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4858">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4858">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4859">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4859">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4860">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4860">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4861">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4861">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4862">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4862">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4863">13 文字の英数字パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4863">13 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4864">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4864">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4865">13 文字の英数字パターン:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4865">13 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4866">2 文字 - FR (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4866">two letters  - FR (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4867">オプションのスペースまたはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4867">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4868">2 文字または数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4868">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4869">オプションのスペース、ドット、ハイフン、またはコンマ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4869">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4870">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4870">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4871">オプションのスペース、ドット、ハイフン、またはコンマ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4871">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4872">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4872">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4873">オプションのスペース、ドット、ハイフン、またはコンマ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4873">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4874">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4874">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4875">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4875">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4876">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4876">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4877">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4877">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4878">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4878">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4879">この関数はFunc_france_value_added_tax_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4879">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4880">ユーザーからのキーワードKeywords_france_value_added_tax_number見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4880">A keyword from Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4881">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4881">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4882">この関数はFunc_france_value_added_tax_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4882">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="949121e6-ad9f-4379-8731-710342baea78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4895">ドイツの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4895">Germany driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4896">この機密情報の種類エンティティは、EU ドライバーのライセンス番号の機密情報の種類に含まれています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4896">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4897">また、スタンドアロンの機密情報の種類エンティティとして利用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4897">It's also available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4898">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4898">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4899">11 桁の数字と文字の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4899">combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4900">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4900">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4901">11 桁の数字と文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4901">11 digits and letters (not case-sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4902">数字または文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4902">a digit or letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4903">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4903">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4904">6 桁の数字または文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4904">six digits or letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4905">数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4905">a digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4906">数字または文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4906">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4907">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4907">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4908">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4908">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4909">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4909">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4910">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4910">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4911">関数 Func_german_drivers_license がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4911">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4912">Keyword_german_drivers_license_number のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4912">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-4913">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-4913">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5062">ドイツの ID カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5062">Germany identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5063">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5063">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5064">2010 年 11 月 1 日以降: 9 文字と数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5064">since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5065">1987 年 4 月 1 日から 2010 年 10 月 31 日まで: 10 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5065">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5066">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5066">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5067">2010 年 11 月 1 日以降:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5067">since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5068">1 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5068">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5069">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5069">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5070">1987 年 4 月 1 日から 2010 年 10 月 31 日まで:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5070">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5071">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5071">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5072">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5072">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5073">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5073">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5074">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5074">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5075">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5075">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5076">正規表現は、Regex_germany_id_card一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5076">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5077">ユーザーからのキーワードKeyword_germany_id_card見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5077">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5078">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5078">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5079">Keyword_germany_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5079">Keyword_germany_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5081">gpid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5081">gpid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5082">ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5082">identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5083">identifikation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5083">identifikation</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5084">identifizierungsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5084">identifizierungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5085">Identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5085">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5086">ID 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5086">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5087">id-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5087">id-nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5088">個人用 ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5088">personal id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5089">personalausweis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5089">personalausweis</span></span>

## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5093">ドイツのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5093">Germany passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5094">このエンティティは、EU Passport Number 機密情報の種類に含まれており、スタンドアロンの機密情報の種類エンティティとして使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5094">This entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5095">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5095">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5096">10 桁の数字または文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5096">10 digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5097">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5097">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5098">パターンには、以下のすべてが含まれる必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5098">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5099">最初の文字は、このセットの数字または文字です (C、F、G、H、J、K)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5099">first character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5100">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5100">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5101">このセットから 5 桁の数字または文字 (C、-H、J-N、P、R、T、V-Z)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5101">five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5102">数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5102">a digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5103">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5103">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5104">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5104">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5105">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5105">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5106">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5106">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5107">関数 Func_german_passport がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5107">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5108">キーワードが見 `Keyword_german_passport` `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5108">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5109">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5109">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5110">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5110">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5111">関数 Func_german_passport_data がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5111">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5112">キーワードが見 `Keyword_german_passport` `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5112">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5113">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5113">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5126">パスポート#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5126">passport#</span></span>

## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5136">ドイツの納税者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5136">Germany tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5137">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5137">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5138">スペースと区切り記号のない 11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5138">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5139">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5139">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5140">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5140">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5141">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5141">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5142">省略可能なスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5142">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5143">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5143">Three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5144">省略可能なスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5144">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5145">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5145">Three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5146">省略可能なスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5146">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5147">2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5147">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5148">1 つのチェックディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5148">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5149">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5149">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5150">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5150">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5151">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5151">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5152">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5152">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5153">この関数  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5153">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5154">キーワードが  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5154">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5155">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5155">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5156">この関数  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5156">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="43316a89-9880-40cf-b980-04bc7eefcec5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5157">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5157">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5158">Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5158">Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5159">identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5159">identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5160">steuer id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5160">steuer id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5161">steueridentifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5161">steueridentifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5162">steuernummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5162">steuernummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5163">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5163">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5164">税の識別なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5164">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5165">税の識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5165">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5166">tax no#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5166">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5167">tax no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5167">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5168">税番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5168">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5169">税登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5169">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5170">タクシー#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5170">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5171">taxidno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5171">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5172">taxidnumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5172">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5173">taxno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5173">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5174">taxnumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5174">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5175">taxnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5175">taxnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5176">tin id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5176">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5177">tin いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5177">tin no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5178">tin#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5178">tin#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5179">zinn#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5179">zinn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5180">zinn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5180">zinn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5181">zinnnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5181">zinnnummer</span></span>


## <a name="germany-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5182">ドイツの付加価値税番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5182">Germany value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5183">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5183">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5184">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5184">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5185">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5185">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5186">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5186">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5187">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5187">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5188">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5188">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5189">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5189">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5190">11 文字の英数字パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5190">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5191">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5191">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5192">11 文字の英数字パターン:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5192">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5193">文字 D または d</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5193">a letter D or d</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5194">E または e の文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5194">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5195">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5195">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5196">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5196">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5197">省略可能なスペースまたはコンマ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5197">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5198">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5198">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5199">省略可能なスペースまたはコンマ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5199">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5200">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5200">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5201">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5201">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5202">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5202">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5203">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5203">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5204">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5204">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5205">この関数Func_germany_value_added_tax_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5205">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5206">ユーザーのキーワードKeywords_germany_value_added_tax_number見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5206">A keyword from Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5207">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5207">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5208">この関数Func_germany_value_added_tax_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5208">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="db177eb2-8811-4842-bffc-128c14aa219f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5218">ギリシャの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5218">Greece driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5219">このエンティティは、EU ドライバーのライセンス番号の機密情報の種類に含まれています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5219">This entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5220">また、スタンドアロンの機密情報の種類エンティティとして使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5220">It is also available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5221">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5221">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5222">スペースと区切り記号のない 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5222">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5223">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5223">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5224">9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5224">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5225">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5225">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5226">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5226">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5227">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5227">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5228">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5228">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5229">正規表現は、  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5229">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5230">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5230">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="7a2200b5-aacf-4e3c-ab36-136d3e68b7da" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-national-id-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5356">ギリシャの国民 ID カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5356">Greece national ID card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5357">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5357">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5358">7 ～ 8 桁の文字と数字の組み合わせとハイフン 1 つ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5358">Combination of 7-8 letters and numbers plus a dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5359">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5359">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5360">7 桁の文字と数字 (従来の形式):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5360">Seven letters and numbers (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5361">1 桁の文字 (ギリシャ語のアルファベット文字) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5361">One letter (any letter of the Greek alphabet)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5362">ハイフン 1 つ </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5362">A dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5363">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5363">Six digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5364">8 桁の文字と数字 (現在の形式):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5364">Eight letters and numbers (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5365">ギリシャ語にもラテン語にも大文字がある文字 (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX) を使用した 2 桁の文字 </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5365">Two letters whose uppercase character occurs in both the Greek and Latin alphabets (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5366">ハイフン 1 つ </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5366">A dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5367">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5367">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5368">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5368">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5369">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5369">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5370">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5370">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5371">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5371">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5372">正規表現は、Regex_greece_id_card一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5372">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5373">ユーザーのキーワードKeyword_greece_id_card見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5373">A keyword from Keyword_greece_id_card is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5374">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5374">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5375">正規表現は、Regex_greece_id_card一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5375">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece National ID Card -->
      <Entity id="82568215-1da1-46d3-874a-d2294d81b5ac" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5376">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5376">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_greece_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5377">Keyword_greece_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5377">Keyword_greece_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5378">ギリシャ語 ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5378">greek id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5379">ギリシャ語の国 ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5379">greek national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5380">ギリシャの個人用 ID カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5380">greek personal id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5381">ギリシャの警察 ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5381">greek police id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5382">Identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5382">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5383">tautotita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5383">tautotita</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5384">ταυτότητα</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5384">ταυτότητα</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5385">ταυτότητας</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5385">ταυτότητας</span></span>


## <a name="greece-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5386">ギリシャのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5386">Greece passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5387">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5387">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5388">2 文字の後に 7 桁の数字が続き、スペースまたは区切り記号は使用されません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5388">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5389">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5389">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5390">2 桁の文字の後に 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5390">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5391">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5391">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5392">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5392">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5393">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5393">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5394">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5394">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5395">正規表現は、  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5395">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5396">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5396">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5397">正規表現は `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` 、DD MMM YY (例 - 8 月 19 日) の形式で日付を検索するか、キーワードが `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5397">The regular expression `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM YY (Example - 28 Aug 19) or a keyword from `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5398">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5398">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5399">正規表現は、  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5399">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5400">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5400">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7e65eb47-cdf9-4f52-8f90-2a27d5ee67e3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5406">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5406">passports</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5413">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5413">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5414">αριθμός διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5414">αριθμός διαβατηρίου</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5416">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5416">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span></span>


## <a name="greece-social-security-number-amka"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5417">ギリシャの社会保障番号 (AMKA)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5417">Greece Social Security Number (AMKA)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5418">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5418">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5419">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5419">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5420">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5420">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5421">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5421">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5422">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5422">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5423">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5423">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5424">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5424">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5425">スペースと区切り記号のない 11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5425">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5426">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5426">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5427">生年月日 YYMMDD として 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5427">Six digits as date of birth YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5428">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5428">Four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5429">チェックの数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5429">a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5430">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5430">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5431">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5431">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5432">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5432">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5433">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5433">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5434">この関数  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5434">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5435">キーワードが  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5435">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5436">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5436">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5437">この関数  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5437">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece Social Security Number (AMKA) -->
      <Entity id="e39b03f4-50ea-41ae-af7a-a4b9539596ad" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5438">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5438">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5439">Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5439">Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5440">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5440">ssn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5441">ssn#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5441">ssn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5442">社会保障なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5442">social security no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5443">socialsecurityno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5443">socialsecurityno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5444">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5444">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5445">amka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5445">amka</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5446">a.m.k.a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5446">a.m.k.a.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5447">Αριθμού Μητρώου Κοινωνικής Ασφάλισης</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5447">Αριθμού Μητρώου Κοινωνικής Ασφάλισης</span></span>


## <a name="greece-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5448">ギリシャの納税者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5448">Greece tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5449">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5449">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5450">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5450">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5451">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5451">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5452">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5452">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5453">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5453">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5454">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5454">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5455">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5455">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5456">スペースと区切り記号のない 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5456">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5457">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5457">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5458">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5458">Nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5459">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5459">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5460">該当しない</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5460">Not applicable</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5461">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5461">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5462">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5462">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5463">正規表現は、  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5463">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5464">キーワードが  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5464">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greek Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="15a54a5a-53d4-4080-ad43-a2a4fe1d3bf7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hong-kong-identity-card-hkid-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5493">香港の ID カード (HKID) 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5493">Hong Kong identity card (HKID) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5494">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5494">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5495">8 ～ 9 桁の文字と数字の組み合わせ、最後の文字はかっこで囲むことも可能</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5495">Combination of 8-9 letters and numbers plus optional parentheses around the final character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5496">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5496">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5497">8 ～ 9 桁の文字の組み合わせ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5497">Combination of 8-9 letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5498">1 ~ 2 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5498">1-2 letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5499">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5499">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5500">チェック ディジットとして機能する最後の文字 (任意の数字か文字 A) はかっこで囲むことも可能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5500">The final character (any digit or the letter A), which is the check digit and is optionally enclosed in parentheses.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5501">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5501">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5502">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5502">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5503">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5503">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5504">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5504">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5505">この関数はFunc_hong_kong_id_card一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5505">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5506">ユーザーからのキーワードKeyword_hong_kong_id_card見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5506">A keyword from Keyword_hong_kong_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5507">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5507">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5508">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5508">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5509">この関数はFunc_hong_kong_id_card一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5509">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5510">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5510">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Hong Kong Identity Card (HKID) number -->
<Entity id="e63c28a7-ad29-4c17-a41a-3d2a0b70fd9c" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5511">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5511">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_hong_kong_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5512">Keyword_hong_kong_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5512">Keyword_hong_kong_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5513">hkid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5513">hkid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5514">香港の ID カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5514">hong kong identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5515">HKIDC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5515">HKIDC</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5516">id card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5516">id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5517">Identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5517">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5518">hk ID カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5518">hk identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5519">香港 ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5519">hong kong id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5520">香港身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5520">香港身份證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5521">香港永久性居民身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5521">香港永久性居民身份證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5522">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5522">身份證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5523">身份証</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5523">身份証</span></span>

## <a name="hungary-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5550">ハンガリーの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5550">Hungary driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5551">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5551">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5552">2 文字の後に 6 桁の数字が続く</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5552">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5553">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5553">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5554">2 文字と 6 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5554">Two letters and six digits:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5555">2 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5555">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5556">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5556">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5557">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5557">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5558">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5558">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5559">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5559">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5560">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5560">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5561">正規表現は、  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5561">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5562">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5562">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <Entity id="9d31c46b-6e6b-444c-aeb1-6dd7e604bb24" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
