## <a name="hungary-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5687">ハンガリーの個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5687">Hungary personal identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5688">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5688">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5689">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5689">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5690">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5690">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5691">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5691">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5692">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5692">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5693">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5693">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5694">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5694">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5695">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5695">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5696">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5696">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5697">11 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5697">11 digits:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5698">性別に対応する 1 桁、男性の場合は 1、女性の場合は 2 桁。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5698">One digit that corresponds to gender, 1 for male, 2 for female.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5699">1900 年以前に生まれた市民や二重国籍を持つ市民の場合も、その他の番号を使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5699">Other numbers are also possible for citizens born before 1900 or citizens with double citizenship.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5700">生年月日に対応する 6 桁の数字 (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5700">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5701">シリアル番号に対応する 3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5701">Three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5702">1 つのチェックディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5702">One check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5703">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5703">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5704">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5704">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5705">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5705">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5706">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5706">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5707">この関数  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5707">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5708">キーワードが  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5708">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5709">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5709">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5710">この関数  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5710">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungary Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="7b5cc218-7046-47d9-80c9-f325b50896ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5711">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5711">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5712">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5712">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5713">id 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5713">id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5714">identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5714">identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5715">sz ig</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5715">sz ig</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5716">sz。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5716">sz.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5717">ig.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5717">ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5718">sz.ig.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5718">sz.ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5719">személyazonosító igazolvány</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5719">személyazonosító igazolvány</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5720">személyi igazolvány</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5720">személyi igazolvány</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5721">ハンガリーのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5721">Hungary passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5722">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5722">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5723">2 つの文字の後に 6 桁または 7 桁の数字が続き、スペースまたは区切り記号はありません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5723">Two letters followed by six or seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5724">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5724">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5725">2 文字の後に 6 桁または 7 桁の数字が続く</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5725">Two letters followed by six or seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5726">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5726">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5727">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5727">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5728">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5728">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5729">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5729">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5730">正規表現は、  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5730">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5731">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5731">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5732">正規表現は `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` 、DD MMM/MMM YY (例 - 01 MÁR/MAR 12) 形式の日付を検索するか、キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5732">The regular expression `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YY (Example - 01 MÁR/MAR 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5733">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5733">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5734">正規表現は、  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5734">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5735">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5735">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungary Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5b483910-9aa7-4c99-9917-f4001464bda7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5736">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5736">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5737">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5737">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5738">パスポート#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5738">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5739">パスポート#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5739">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5740">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5740">passportid</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5742">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5742">passportno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5743">パスポートなし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5743">passport no</span></span>

## <a name="hungary-social-security-number-taj"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5755">ハンガリーの社会保障番号 (TAJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5755">Hungary social security number (TAJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5756">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5756">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5757">スペースと区切り記号のない 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5757">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5758">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5758">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5759">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5759">Nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5760">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5760">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5761">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5761">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5762">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5762">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5763">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5763">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5764">この関数  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5764">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5765">キーワードが  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5765">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5766">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5766">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5767">この関数  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5767">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Social Security Number (TAJ) -->
      <Entity id="0de78315-9537-47f5-95ab-b3e77eba3993" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5787">ハンガリーの納税者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5787">Hungary tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5788">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5788">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5789">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5789">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5790">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5790">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5791">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5791">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5792">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5792">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5793">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5793">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5794">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5794">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5795">スペースまたは区切り記号がない 10 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5795">10 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5796">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5796">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5797">10 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5797">10 digits:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5798">"8" である必要があります 1 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5798">One digit that must be "8"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5799">8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5799">Eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5800">1 つのチェックディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5800">One check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5801">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5801">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5802">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5802">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5803">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5803">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5804">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5804">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5805">この関数  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5805">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5806">キーワードが  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5806">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5807">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5807">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5808">この関数  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5808">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungary Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="ede42eb4-59d9-49eb-9603-d7853fbda91d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5811">adóazonosító szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5811">adóazonosító szám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5812">adóhatóság szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5812">adóhatóság szám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5813">adószám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5813">adószám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5814">ハンガリーのスズ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5814">hungarian tin</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5815">hungatiantin#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5815">hungatiantin#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5816">税務当局 なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5816">tax authority no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5817">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5817">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5818">税の識別なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5818">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5819">税の識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5819">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5820">tax no#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5820">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5821">tax no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5821">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5822">税番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5822">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5823">税登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5823">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5824">タクシー#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5824">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5825">taxidno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5825">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5826">taxidnumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5826">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5827">taxno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5827">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5828">taxnumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5828">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5829">taxnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5829">taxnumber</span></span>

## <a name="hungary-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5834">ハンガリーの付加価値税番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5834">Hungary value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5835">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5835">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5836">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5836">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5837">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5837">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5838">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5838">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5839">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5839">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5840">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5840">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5841">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5841">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5842">10 文字の英数字パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5842">10 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5843">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5843">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5844">10 文字の英数字パターン:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5844">10 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5845">2 文字 - HU または hu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5845">two letters - HU or hu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5846">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5846">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5847">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5847">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5848">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5848">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5849">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5849">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5850">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5850">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5851">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5851">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5852">この関数はFunc_hungarian_value_added_tax_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5852">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5853">ユーザーのキーワードKeywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5853">A keyword from Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5854">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5854">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5855">この関数はFunc_hungarian_value_added_tax_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5855">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="976349a0-683b-477a-90f8-ff0a220d5592" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5856">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5856">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_hungary_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5857">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5857">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5858">vat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5858">vat</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5859">付加価値税番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5859">value added tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5860">vat#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5860">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5861">vatno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5861">vatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5862">hungarianvatno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5862">hungarianvatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5863">tax no.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5863">tax no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5864">付加価値税 áfa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5864">value added tax áfa</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5867">hozzáadottérték adó</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5867">hozzáadottérték adó</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5868">áfa szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5868">áfa szám</span></span>


## <a name="india-permanent-account-number-pan"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5869">インドの永続的なアカウント番号 (PAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5869">India permanent account number (PAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5870">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5870">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5871">10 桁の文字または数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5871">10 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5872">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5872">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5873">10 桁の文字または数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5873">10 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5874">3 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5874">Three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5875">C、P、H、F、A、T、B、L、J、G の文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5875">A letter in C, P, H, F, A, T, B, L, J, G (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5876">レター</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5876">A letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5877">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5877">Four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5878">英字チェックの数字である文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5878">A letter that is an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5879">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5879">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5880">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5880">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5881">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5881">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5882">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5882">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5883">正規表現は、Regex_india_permanent_account_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5883">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5884">ユーザーからのキーワードKeyword_india_permanent_account_number見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5884">A keyword from Keyword_india_permanent_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5885">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5885">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5886">正規表現は、Regex_india_permanent_account_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5886">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- India Permanent Account Number -->
      <Entity id="2602bfee-9bb0-47a5-a7a6-2bf3053e2804" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_india_permanent_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3520.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5887">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5887">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_india_permanent_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5888">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5888">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5889">Permanent Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5889">Permanent Account Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5890">PAN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5890">PAN</span></span>

## <a name="india-unique-identification-aadhaar-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5891">インドの一意の ID (Aadhaar) 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5891">India unique identification (Aadhaar) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5892">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5892">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5893">省略可能なスペースまたはハイフンを含む 12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5893">12 digits containing optional spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5894">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5894">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5895">12 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5895">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5896">0 または 1 ではない数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5896">A digit which is not 0 or 1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5897">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5897">Three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5898">スペースまたはハイフン 1 つ (省略可能) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5898">An optional space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5899">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5899">Four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5900">スペースまたはハイフン 1 つ (省略可能) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5900">An optional space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5901">最後の数字 (チェック桁)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5901">The final digit, which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5902">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5902">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5903">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5903">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5904">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5904">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5905">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5905">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5906">この関数Func_india_aadhaar一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5906">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5907">ユーザーのキーワードKeyword_india_aadhar見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5907">A keyword from Keyword_india_aadhar is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5908">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5908">The checksum passes.</span></span>
-
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5909">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5909">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5910">この関数Func_india_aadhaar一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5910">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5911">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5911">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- India Unique Identification (Aadhaar) number -->
<Entity id="1ca46b29-76f5-4f46-9383-cfa15e91048f" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_india_aadhar"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5912">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5912">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_india_aadhar"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5913">Keyword_india_aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5913">Keyword_india_aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5914">aadhaar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5914">aadhaar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5915">aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5915">aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5916">aadhar#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5916">aadhar#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5917">uid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5917">uid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5918">आधार</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5918">आधार</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5919">uidai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5919">uidai</span></span>

## <a name="indonesia-identity-card-ktp-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5920">インドネシアの ID カード (KTP) 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5920">Indonesia identity card (KTP) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5921">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5921">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5922">省略可能なピリオドを含む 16 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5922">16 digits containing optional periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5923">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5923">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5924">16 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5924">16 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5925">2 桁の行政区コード </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5925">Two-digit province code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5926">ピリオド 1 つ (省略可能) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5926">A period (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5927">2 桁の行政区または市コード </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5927">Two-digit regency or city code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5928">2 桁の分区コード </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5928">Two-digit subdistrict code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5929">ピリオド 1 つ (省略可能) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5929">A period (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5930">DDMMYY という形式の 6 桁の数字 (生年月日)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5930">Six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5931">ピリオド 1 つ (省略可能) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5931">A period (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5932">4 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5932">Four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5933">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5933">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5934">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5934">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5935">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5935">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5936">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5936">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5937">正規表現は、Regex_indonesia_id_card一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5937">The regular expression Regex_indonesia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5938">ユーザーからのキーワードKeyword_indonesia_id_card見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5938">A keyword from Keyword_indonesia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Indonesia Identity Card (KTP) Number -->
<Entity id="da68fdb0-f383-4981-8c86-82689d3b7d55" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_indonesia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_indonesia_id_card"/>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5939">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5939">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_indonesia_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5940">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5940">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5941">KTP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5941">KTP</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5943">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5943">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span></span>

## <a name="international-banking-account-number-iban"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5944">国際銀行口座番号 (IBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5944">International banking account number (IBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5945">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5945">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5946">国コード (2 文字) プラスチェックの数字 (2 桁) プラス bban 番号 (最大 30 文字)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5946">Country code (two letters) plus check digits (two digits) plus bban number (up to 30 characters)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5947">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5947">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5948">パターンには、以下のすべてが含まれる必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5948">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5949">2 文字の国コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5949">Two-letter country code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5950">2 桁のチェック数字 (その後にオプションのスペース)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5950">Two check digits (followed by an optional space)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5951">4 つの文字または数字の 1 ~ 7 グループ (スペースで区切って指定できます)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5951">1-7 groups of four letters or digits (can be separated by spaces)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5952">1 ～ 3 個の文字または数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5952">1-3 letters or digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5953">国ごとに形式が若干異なります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5953">The format for each country is slightly different.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5954">IBAN の機密情報の種類は、次の 60 か国を対象とします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5954">The IBAN sensitive information type covers these 60 countries:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-5983">すなわち</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-5983">ie</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6003">pl</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6003">pl</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6004">pt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6004">pt</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6005">ro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6005">ro</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6006">rs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6006">rs</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6007">sa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6007">sa</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6015">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6015">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6016">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6016">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6017">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6017">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6018">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6018">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6019">関数 Func_iban がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6019">The function Func_iban finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6020">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6020">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="e7dc4711-11b7-4cb0-b88b-2c394a771f0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_iban" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6021">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6021">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6022">なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6022">None</span></span>


## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-10-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6023">病気の国際分類 (ICD-10-CM)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6023">International classification of diseases (ICD-10-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6024">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6024">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6025">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6025">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6026">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6026">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6027">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6027">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6028">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6028">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6029">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6029">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6030">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6030">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6031">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6031">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6032">ユーザーからのキーワードDictionary_icd_10_updated見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6032">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6033">ユーザーのキーワードDictionary_icd_10_codes見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6033">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6034">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6034">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6035">更新されたDictionary_icd_10_キーワードが見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6035">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_ updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- ICD-10 CM -->
      <Entity id="3356946c-6bb7-449b-b253-6ffa419c0ce7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
        </Pattern>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6036">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6036">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6037">病気の国際分類、第 10 リビジョン、臨床変更 [(ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604)に基づく、Dictionary_icd_10_updated キーワード 辞書の任意の用語。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6037">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6038">この型は、保険コードではなく、用語のみを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6038">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6039">病気の国際分類、第 10 リビジョン、臨床変更 [(ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604)に基づく、Dictionary_icd_10_codes キーワード 辞書の任意の用語。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6039">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6040">この型は、説明ではなく、保険コードのみを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6040">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-9-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6041">病気の国際分類 (ICD-9-CM)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6041">International classification of diseases (ICD-9-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6042">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6042">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6043">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6043">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6044">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6044">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6045">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6045">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6046">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6046">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6047">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6047">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6048">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6048">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6049">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6049">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6050">このページのDictionary_icd_9_updatedが見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6050">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6051">ユーザーのキーワードDictionary_icd_9_codes見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6051">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6052">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6052">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6053">このページのDictionary_icd_9_updatedが見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6053">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <Entity id="fa3f9c74-ee07-4c52-b5f2-085d6b2c0ec4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6054">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6054">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6055">病気の国際分類、第 9 改訂、臨床変更 [(ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)に基づく、Dictionary_icd_9_updated キーワード 辞書からの任意の用語。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6055">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6056">この型は、保険コードではなく、用語のみを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6056">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

## <a name="ip-address"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6059">IP アドレス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6059">IP address</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6060">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6060">Format</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv4"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6061">IPv4:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6061">IPv4:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6062">IPv4 アドレスの書式付き (ピリオド) バージョンと書式設定されていない (ピリオドなし) バージョンをアカウントする複雑なパターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6062">Complex pattern that accounts for formatted (periods) and unformatted (no periods) versions of the IPv4 addresses</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv6"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6063">IPv6:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6063">IPv6:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6064">書式設定された IPv6 番号を表す複雑なパターン (コロンを含む)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6064">Complex pattern that accounts for formatted IPv6 numbers (which include colons)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6065">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6065">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6066">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6066">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6067">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6067">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6068">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6068">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6069">IPv6 の場合、DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6069">For IPv6, a DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6070">正規表現 Regex_ipv6_address がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6070">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6071">Keyword_ipaddress のキーワードを検出しなかった。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6071">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6072">IPv4 の場合、DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6072">For IPv4, a DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6073">正規表現 Regex_ipv4_address がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6073">The regular expression Regex_ipv4_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6074">Keyword_ipaddress のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6074">A keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6075">IPv6 の場合、DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6075">For IPv6, a DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6076">正規表現 Regex_ipv6_address がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6076">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6077">Keyword_ipaddress のキーワードを検出しなかった。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6077">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- IP Address -->
    <Entity id="1daa4ad5-e2dd-4ca4-a788-54722c09efb2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv4_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6078">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6078">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ipaddress"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6079">Keyword_ipaddress</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6079">Keyword_ipaddress</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6080">IP (このキーワードでは大文字と小文字が区別されます)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6080">IP (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6081">ip address</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6081">ip address</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6082">ip addresses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6082">ip addresses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6083">internet protocol</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6083">internet protocol</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6084">IP-כתובת ה</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6084">IP-כתובת ה</span></span>

## <a name="ireland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6085">アイルランドの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6085">Ireland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6086">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6086">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6087">6 桁の数字の後に 4 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6087">Six digits followed by four letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6088">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6088">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6089">6 桁の数字と 4 文字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6089">Six digits and four letters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6090">6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6090">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6091">4 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6091">Four letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6092">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6092">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6093">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6093">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6094">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6094">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6095">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6095">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6096">正規表現は、  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6096">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6097">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6097">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ireland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="e01bccd9-eb4d-414f-ace1-e9b6a4c4a2ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6221">アイルランドのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6221">Ireland passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6222">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6222">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6223">2 つの文字または数字の後に、スペースまたは区切り記号がない 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6223">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6224">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6224">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6225">2 つの文字または数字の後に 7 桁の数字が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6225">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6226">2 桁または 1 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6226">Two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6227">7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6227">Seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6228">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6228">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6229">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6229">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6230">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6230">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6231">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6231">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6232">正規表現は、  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6232">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6233">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6233">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6234">正規表現は `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` 、DD MMM/MMM YYYY (例 - 01 BEA/MAY 1988) の形式で日付を検索するか、キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6234">The regular expression `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 BEA/MAY 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6235">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6235">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6236">正規表現は、  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6236">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6237">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6237">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ireland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="a2130f27-9ee2-4103-84f9-a6b1ee7d0cbf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-personal-public-service-pps-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6261">アイルランドの個人公開サービス (PPS) 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6261">Ireland personal public service (PPS) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6262">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6262">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6263">古い形式 (2012 年 12 月 31 日まで):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6263">Old format (until 31 December 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6264">7 桁の数字の後に 1 ~ 2 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6264">seven digits followed by 1-2 letters</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6265">新しい形式 (2013 年 1 月 1 日以降):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6265">New format (1 January 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6266">7 桁の数字の後に 2 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6266">seven digits followed by two letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6267">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6267">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6268">古い形式 (2012 年 12 月 31 日まで):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6268">Old format (until 31 December 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6269">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6269">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6270">1 ~ 2 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6270">one to two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6271">新しい形式 (2013 年 1 月 1 日以降):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6271">New format (1 January 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6272">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6272">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6273">英字チェックの数字である文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6273">a letter (not case-sensitive) which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6274">範囲 A から I、または "W" のオプションの文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6274">An optional letter in the range A-I, or “W”</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6275">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6275">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6276">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6276">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6277">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6277">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6278">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6278">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6279">この関数はFunc_ireland_pps一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6279">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6280">ユーザーからのキーワードKeywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6280">A keyword from Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6281">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6281">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6282">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6282">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6283">この関数はFunc_ireland_pps一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6283">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6284">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6284">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ireland Personal Public Service (PPS) Number -->
      <Entity id="1cdb674d-c19a-4fcf-9f4b-7f56cc87345a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
