## <a name="israel-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6329">イスラエルの銀行口座番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6329">Israel bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6330">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6330">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6331">13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6331">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6332">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6332">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6333">書式設定:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6333">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6334">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6334">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6335">ダッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6335">a dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6336">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6336">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6337">ダッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6337">a dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6338">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6338">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6339">Unformatted:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6339">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6340">	13 桁の連続する数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6340">13 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6341">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6341">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6342">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6342">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6343">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6343">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6344">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6344">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6345">正規表現 Regex_israel_bank_account_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6345">The regular expression Regex_israel_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6346">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6346">A keyword from Keyword_israel_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="7d08b2ff-a0b9-437f-957c-aeddbf9b2b25" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_israel_bank_account_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_israel_bank_account_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6347">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6347">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6348">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6348">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6349">Bank Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6349">Bank Account Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6350">Bank Account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6350">Bank Account</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6351">Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6351">Account Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6352">מספר חשבון בנק</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6352">מספר חשבון בנק</span></span>

## <a name="israel-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6353">イスラエルの国民識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6353">Israel national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6354">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6354">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6355">9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6355">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6356">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6356">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6357">9 桁の連続する数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6357">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6358">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6358">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6359">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6359">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6360">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6360">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6361">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6361">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6362">関数 Func_israeli_national_id_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6362">The function Func_israeli_national_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6363">Keyword_Israel_National_ID のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6363">A keyword from Keyword_Israel_National_ID is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6364">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6364">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel National ID Number -->
<Entity id="e05881f5-1db1-418c-89aa-a3ac5c5277ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_israeli_national_id_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Israel_National_ID" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6365">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6365">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6366">Keyword_Israel_National_ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6366">Keyword_Israel_National_ID</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6367">מספר זהות</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6367">מספר זהות</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6368">מספר זיה וי</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6368">מספר זיה וי</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6369">מספר זיהוי ישר אלי</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6369">מספר זיהוי ישר אלי</span></span>      
-   <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6370">זהותישר אלית</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6370">זהותישר אלית</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6371">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6371">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6372">هوية إسرائ يلية</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6372">هوية إسرائ يلية</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6373">رقم الهوية</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6373">رقم الهوية</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6374">عدد هوية فريدة من نوعها</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6374">عدد هوية فريدة من نوعها</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6375">idnumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6375">idnumber#</span></span>

## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6383">イタリアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6383">Italy driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6384">この種類のエンティティは、EU ドライバーのライセンス番号の機密情報の種類に含まれています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6384">This type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6385">また、スタンドアロンの機密情報の種類エンティティとして使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6385">It is also available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6386">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6386">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6387">10 文字と数字の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6387">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6388">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6388">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6389">10 文字と数字の組み合わせ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6389">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6390">1 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6390">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6391">文字 "A" または "V" (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6391">the letter "A" or "V" (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6392">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6392">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6393">1 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6393">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6394">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6394">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6395">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6395">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6396">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6396">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6397">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6397">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6398">正規表現は、 `Regex_italy_drivers_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6398">The regular expression `Regex_italy_drivers_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6399">キーワードが見 `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6399">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
    <Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-fiscal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6526">イタリアの会計コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6526">Italy fiscal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6527">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6527">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6528">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6528">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6529">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6529">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6530">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6530">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6531">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6531">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6532">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6532">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6533">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6533">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6534">指定したパターンの文字と数字の 16 文字の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6534">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6535">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6535">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6536">16 文字の文字と数字の組み合わせ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6536">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6537">ファミリ名の最初の 3 つの子文字に対応する 3 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6537">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6538">最初の名前、3 番目、4 番目の子名に対応する 3 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6538">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6539">出生年の最後の数字に対応する 2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6539">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6540">出生月の文字に対応する 1 つの文字 - 文字はアルファベット順で使用されますが、A から E、H、L、M、P、R から T の文字だけが使用されます (したがって、1 月は A で、10 月は R です)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6540">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (so, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6541">性別を区別するために、出生日に対応する 2 桁の数字、女性の出生日に 40 が追加されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6541">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6542">人が生まれた市区町村に固有の市外コードに対応する 4 桁の数字 (国全体のコードは外国で使用されます)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6542">four digits that correspond to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6543">1 つのパリティディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6543">one parity digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6544">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6544">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6545">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6545">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6546">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6546">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6547">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6547">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6548">この関数  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6548">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6549">キーワードが  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6549">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6550">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6550">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6551">この関数  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6551">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6586">イタリアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6586">Italy passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6587">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6587">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6588">2 つの文字または数字の後にスペースまたは区切り記号を付けない 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6588">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6589">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6589">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6590">2 つの文字または数字の後に 7 桁の数字が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6590">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6591">2 桁の数字または文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6591">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6592">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6592">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6593">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6593">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6594">該当なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6594">not applicable</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6595">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6595">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6596">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6596">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6597">正規表現は、  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6597">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6598">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6598">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6599">正規表現は `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` 、DD MMM/MMM YYYY (例 - 01 GEN/JAN 1988) 形式の日付を検索するか、キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6599">The regular expression `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 GEN/JAN 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6600">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6600">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6601">正規表現は、  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6601">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6602">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6602">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Passport Number -->

          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6626">イタリアの付加価値税番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6626">Italy value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6627">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6627">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6628">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6628">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6629">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6629">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6630">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6630">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6631">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6631">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6632">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6632">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6633">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6633">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6634">13 文字の英数字パターン (オプションの区切り記号付き)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6634">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6635">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6635">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6636">13 文字の英数字パターン (オプションの区切り記号付き):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6636">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6637">I または i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6637">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6638">T または t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6638">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6639">オプションのスペース、ドット、ハイフン、またはコンマ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6639">optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6640">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6640">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6641">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6641">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6642">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6642">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6643">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6643">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6644">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6644">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6645">この関数はFunc_italy_value_added_tax_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6645">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6646">このページのKeywords_italy_value_added_tax_number見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6646">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6647">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6647">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6648">この関数はFunc_italy_value_added_tax_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6648">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6656">日本の銀行口座番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6656">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6657">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6657">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6658">7 桁または 8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6658">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6659">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6659">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6660">銀行口座番号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6660">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6661">7 桁または 8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6661">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6662">銀行口座のブランチ コード:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6662">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6663">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6663">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6664">スペースまたはダッシュ (オプション)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6664">a space or dash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6665">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6665">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6666">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6666">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6667">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6667">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6668">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6668">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6669">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6669">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6670">関数 Func_jp_bank_account がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6670">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6671">Keyword_jp_bank_account のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6671">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6672">次のいずれかの条件に該当する:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6672">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6673">関数 Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6673">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6674">Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6674">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6675">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6675">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6676">関数 Func_jp_bank_account がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6676">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6677">Keyword_jp_bank_account のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6677">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6724">日本の運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6724">Japan driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6725">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6725">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6726">12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6726">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6727">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6727">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6728">12 桁の連続する数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6728">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6729">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6729">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6730">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6730">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6731">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6731">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6732">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6732">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6733">関数 Func_jp_drivers_license_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6733">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6734">Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6734">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6772">日本のマイナンバー - 企業</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6772">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6773">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6773">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6774">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6774">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6775">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6775">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6776">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6776">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6777">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6777">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6778">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6778">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6779">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6779">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6780">13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6780">13-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6781">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6781">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6782">13 桁の番号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6782">13-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6783">1 から 9 の 1 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6783">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6784">12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6784">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6785">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6785">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6786">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6786">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6787">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6787">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6788">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6788">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6789">この関数はFunc_japanese_my_number_corporate一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6789">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6790">ユーザーからのキーワードKeywords_japanese_my_number_corporate見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6790">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6791">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6791">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6792">この関数はFunc_japanese_my_number_corporate一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6792">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6799">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6799">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6805">日本のマイナンバー - 個人用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6805">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6806">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6806">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6807">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6807">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6808">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6808">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6809">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6809">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6810">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6810">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6811">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6811">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6812">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6812">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6813">12 桁の番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6813">12-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6814">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6814">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6815">12 桁の番号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6815">12-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6816">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6816">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6817">オプションのスペース、ドット、またはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6817">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6818">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6818">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6819">オプションのスペース、ドット、またはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6819">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6820">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6820">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6821">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6821">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6822">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6822">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6823">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6823">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6824">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6824">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6825">この関数はFunc_japanese_my_number_personal一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6825">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6826">ユーザーのキーワードKeywords_japanese_my_number_personal見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6826">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6827">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6827">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6828">この関数はFunc_japanese_my_number_personal一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6828">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6829">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6829">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6831">my number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6831">my number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6832">マイナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6832">マイナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6833">個人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6833">個人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6834">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6834">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6835">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6835">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6836">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6836">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6837">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6837">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6838">個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6838">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6839">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6839">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6840">通知カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6840">通知カード</span></span>


## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6841">日本のパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6841">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6842">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6842">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6843">2 文字の後に 7 桁の数字を付け</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6843">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6844">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6844">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6845">2 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません) の後に 7 桁の数字が続く</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6845">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6846">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6846">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6847">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6847">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6848">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6848">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6849">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6849">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6850">関数 Func_jp_passport がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6850">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6851">Keyword_jp_passport のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6851">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6852">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6852">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6853">Keyword_jp_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6853">Keyword_jp_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6854">Passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6854">Passport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6855">Passport Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6855">Passport Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6856">Passport No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6856">Passport No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6857">Passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6857">Passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6858">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6858">パスポート</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6859">パスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6859">パスポート番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6860">パスポートナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6860">パスポートナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6861">パスポート＃</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6861">パスポート＃</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6862">パスポート#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6862">パスポート#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6863">下に示すのは、1 つの</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6863">パスポートNo.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6864">旅券番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6864">旅券番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6865">旅券番号＃</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6865">旅券番号＃</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6866">旅券番号♯</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6866">旅券番号♯</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6867">旅券ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6867">旅券ナンバー</span></span>


## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6868">日本の在留カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6868">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6869">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6869">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6870">12 文字と数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6870">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6871">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6871">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6872">12 文字と数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6872">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6873">2 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6873">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6874">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6874">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6875">2 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6875">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6876">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6876">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6877">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6877">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6878">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6878">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6879">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6879">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6880">正規表現は、Regex_jp_residence_card_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6880">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6881">ユーザーのキーワードKeyword_jp_residence_card_number見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6881">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6882">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6882">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6883">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6883">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6884">在留カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6884">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6885">在留カードなし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6885">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6886">在留カード#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6886">Residence card #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6887">在留カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6887">在留カード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6888">在留カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6888">在留カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6889">在留番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6889">在留番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6890">日本居住者登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6890">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6891">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6891">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6892">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6892">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6893">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6893">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6894">11 桁の連続する数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6894">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6895">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6895">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6896">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6896">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6897">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6897">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6898">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6898">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6899">関数 Func_jp_resident_registration_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6899">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6900">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6900">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6901">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6901">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_resident_registration_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6902">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6902">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6903">Resident Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6903">Resident Registration Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6904">Residents Basic Registry Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6904">Residents Basic Registry Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6905">Resident Registration No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6905">Resident Registration No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6906">Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6906">Resident Register No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6907">Residents Basic Registry No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6907">Residents Basic Registry No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6908">Basic Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6908">Basic Resident Register No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6909">外国人登録証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6909">外国人登録証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6910">証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6910">証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6911">登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6911">登録番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6912">外国人登録証</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6912">外国人登録証</span></span>


## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6913">日本の社会保険番号 (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6913">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6914">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6914">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6915">7～ 12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6915">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6916">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6916">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6917">7 ～ 12 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6917">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6918">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6918">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6919">ハイフン (オプション)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6919">a hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6920">6 桁の OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6920">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6921">7 ～ 12 桁の連続する数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6921">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6922">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6922">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6923">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6923">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6924">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6924">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6925">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6925">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6926">関数 Func_jp_sin がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6926">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6927">Keyword_jp_sin のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6927">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6928">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6928">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6929">関数 Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6929">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6930">Keyword_jp_sin のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6930">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6951">ラトビアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6951">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6952">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6952">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6953">3 文字の後に 6 桁の数字が続く</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6953">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6954">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6954">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6955">3 文字と 6 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6955">three letters and six digits:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6956">3 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6956">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6957">6 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6957">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6958">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6958">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6959">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6959">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6960">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6960">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6961">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6961">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6962">正規表現は、  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6962">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-6963">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-6963">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7088">ラトビアの個人用コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7088">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7089">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7089">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7090">11 桁の数字とオプションのハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7090">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7091">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7091">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7092">古い形式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7092">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7093">11 桁の数字とハイフン:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7093">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7094">生年月日に対応する 6 桁の数字 (DDMMYY)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7094">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7095">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7095">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7096">生後世紀に対応する 1 桁の数字 (19 世紀は "0"、20 世紀は "1"、21 世紀は "2")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7096">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7097">4 桁の数字、ランダムに生成される</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7097">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7098">新しい形式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7098">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7099">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7099">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7100">2 桁の "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7100">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7101">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7101">Nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7102">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7102">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7103">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7103">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7104">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7104">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7105">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7105">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7106">関数または  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` 正規表現は、 `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7106">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7107">キーワードが  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7107">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7108">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7108">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7109">関数または  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` 正規表現は、 `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7109">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7172">ラトビアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7172">Latvia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7173">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7173">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7174">2 つの文字または数字の後にスペースまたは区切り記号を付けない 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7174">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7175">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7175">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7176">2 つの文字または数字の後に 7 桁の数字が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7176">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7177">2 桁の数字または文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7177">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7178">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7178">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7179">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7179">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7180">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7180">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7181">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7181">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7182">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7182">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7183">正規表現は、  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7183">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7184">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7184">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7185">正規表現が `Regex_eu_passport_date1` DD.MM.YYYYY 形式の日付を検索するか、キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7185">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7186">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7186">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7187">正規表現は、  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7187">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7188">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7188">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Latvia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="23ae25ec-cc28-421b-b77a-3054eadf1ede" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7211">リトアニアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7211">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7212">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7212">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7213">スペースと区切り記号のない 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7213">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7214">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7214">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7215">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7215">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7216">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7216">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7217">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7217">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7218">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7218">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7219">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7219">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7220">正規表現は、  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7220">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7221">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7221">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="86f7628b-e0f4-4dc3-9fbc-e4300e4c7d78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
