## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7346">リトアニアの個人用コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7346">Lithuania personal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7347">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7347">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7348">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7348">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7349">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7349">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7350">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7350">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7351">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7351">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7352">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7352">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7353">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7353">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7354">スペースと区切り記号のない 11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7354">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7355">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7355">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7356">スペースと区切り記号のない 11 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7356">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7357">人の性別と出生世紀に対応する 1 桁の数字 (1 ~ 6)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7357">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7358">生年月日に対応する 6 桁の数字 (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7358">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7359">生年月日のシリアル番号に対応する 3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7359">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7360">1 つのチェックディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7360">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7361">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7361">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7362">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7362">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7363">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7363">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7364">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7364">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7365">この関数  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7365">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7366">キーワードが  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7366">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7367">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7367">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7368">この関数  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7368">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7403">リトアニアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7403">Lithuania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7404">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7404">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7405">スペースまたは区切り記号を含む 8 桁の数字または文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7405">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7406">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7406">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7407">8 桁の数字または文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7407">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7408">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7408">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7409">該当なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7409">not applicable</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7410">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7410">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7411">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7411">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7412">正規表現は、  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7412">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7413">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7413">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7414">正規表現が DD MM YYYY の形式で日付を検索するか、キーワード `Regex_eu_passport_date3` が `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかった</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7414">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7415">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7415">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7416">正規表現は、  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7416">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7417">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7417">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1b79900f-047b-4c3f-846f-7d73b5534bce" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7437">ルクセンブルクの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7437">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7438">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7438">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7439">スペースと区切り記号のない 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7439">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7440">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7440">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7441">6 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7441">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7442">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7442">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7443">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7443">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7444">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7444">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7445">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7445">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7446">正規表現は、  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7446">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7447">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7447">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="89daf717-1544-4860-9a2e-fc9166dd8852" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7571">ルクセンブルクの国民識別番号 (自然人)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7571">Luxemburg national identification number (natural persons)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7572">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7572">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7573">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7573">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7574">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7574">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7575">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7575">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7576">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7576">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7577">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7577">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7578">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7578">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7579">スペースまたは区切り記号がない 13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7579">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7580">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7580">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7581">13 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7581">13 digits:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7582">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7582">11 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7583">2 つのチェックの数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7583">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7584">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7584">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7585">○</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7585">yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7586">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7586">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7587">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7587">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7588">この関数  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7588">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7589">キーワードが  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7589">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7590">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7590">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7591">この関数  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7591">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7592">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7592">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7614">ルクセンブルクのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7614">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7615">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7615">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7616">スペースまたは区切り記号を含む 8 桁の数字または文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7616">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7617">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7617">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7618">8 桁の数字または文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7618">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7619">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7619">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7620">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7620">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7621">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7621">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7622">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7622">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7623">正規表現は、  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7623">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7624">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7624">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7625">正規表現が DD MM YYYY の形式で日付を検索するか、キーワード `Regex_eu_passport_date3` が `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかった</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7625">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7626">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7626">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7627">正規表現は、  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7627">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7628">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7628">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="81d5c027-bed9-4421-91a0-3b2e55b3eb85" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7660">ルクセンブルクの国民識別番号 (非自然人)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7660">Luxemburg national identification number (non-natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7661">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7661">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7662">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7662">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7663">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7663">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7664">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7664">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7665">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7665">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7666">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7666">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7667">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7667">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7668">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7668">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7669">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7669">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7670">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7670">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7671">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7671">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7672">1 つのチェックディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7672">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7673">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7673">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7674">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7674">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7675">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7675">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7676">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7676">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7677">この関数  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7677">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7678">キーワードが  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7678">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7679">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7679">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7680">この関数  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7680">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7720">マレーシアの ID カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7720">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7721">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7721">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7722">省略可能なハイフンを含む 12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7722">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7723">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7723">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7724">12 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7724">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7725">YYMMDD 形式の 6 桁の数字 (生年月日)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7725">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7726">ダッシュ (オプション)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7726">a dash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7727">2 文字の出生場所コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7727">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7728">ダッシュ (オプション)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7728">a dash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7729">3 つのランダムな数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7729">three random digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7730">1 桁の性別コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7730">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7731">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7731">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7732">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7732">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7733">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7733">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7734">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7734">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7735">正規表現は、Regex_malaysia_id_card_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7735">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7736">ユーザーからのキーワードKeyword_malaysia_id_card_number見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7736">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7763">マルタの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7763">Malta driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7764">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7764">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7765">指定したパターンの 2 文字と 6 桁の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7765">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7766">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7766">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7767">2 文字と 6 桁の組み合わせ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7767">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7768">2 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない数字または文字)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7768">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7769">スペース (オプション)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7769">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7770">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7770">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7771">スペース (オプション)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7771">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7772">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7772">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7773">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7773">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7774">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7774">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7775">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7775">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7776">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7776">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7777">正規表現は、  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7777">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7778">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7778">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Malta Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="a3bdaa4a-8371-4735-8fa5-56ee0fb4afc4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7902">マルタの ID カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7902">Malta identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7903">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7903">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7904">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7904">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7905">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7905">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7906">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7906">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7907">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7907">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7908">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7908">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7909">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7909">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7910">7 桁の数字の後に 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7910">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7911">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7911">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7912">7 桁の数字の後に 1 文字が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7912">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7913">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7913">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7914">"M、G、A、P、L、H、B、Z" の 1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7914">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7915">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7915">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7916">該当しない</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7916">Not applicable</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7917">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7917">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7918">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7918">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7919">正規表現は、  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7919">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7920">キーワードが  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7920">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7921">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7921">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7922">正規表現は、  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7922">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7925">市民サービス番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7925">citizen service number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7928">kodiċi数字の個人用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7928">kodiċi numerali personali</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7929">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni personali</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7929">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni personali</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7930">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni tat-taxxa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7930">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7931">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7931">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7933">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7933">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span></span>

## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7939">マルタのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7939">Malta passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7940">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7940">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7941">スペースまたは区切り記号のない 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7941">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7942">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7942">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7943">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7943">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7944">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7944">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7945">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7945">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7946">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7946">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7947">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7947">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7948">正規表現は、  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7948">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7949">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7949">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7950">キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7950">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7951">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7951">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7952">正規表現は、  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7952">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7953">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7953">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Malta Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="b2b21198-48f9-4d13-b2a5-03969bff0fb8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7958">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7958">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7959">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7959">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7960">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7960">passportno</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7967">numru tal-passaport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7967">numru tal-passaport</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_date"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7970">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7970">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span></span>

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7973">マルタの納税者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7973">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7974">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7974">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7975">マルタ国民の場合:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7975">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7976">指定したパターンの 7 桁の数字と 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7976">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7977">マルタ以外の国民およびマルタ人のエンティティ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7977">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7978">9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7978">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7979">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7979">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7980">マルタ国民: 7 桁の数字と 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7980">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7981">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7981">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7982">1 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7982">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7983">マルタ以外の国民およびマルタのエンティティ: 9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7983">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7984">9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7984">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7985">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7985">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7986">該当しない</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7986">Not applicable</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7987">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7987">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7988">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7988">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7989">正規表現または  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  パターン `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` に一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7989">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7990">キーワードが  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7990">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7991">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7991">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7992">正規表現または  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` パターン `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` に一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7992">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7993">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7993">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7994">Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7994">Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-7998">kodiċi数字の個人用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-7998">kodiċi numerali personali</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8001">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8001">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8002">numru ta' identità uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8002">numru ta' identità uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8003">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8003">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8004">numru tat-taxxa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8004">numru tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8005">個人の数値コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8005">personal numeric code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8006">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8006">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8007">税の識別なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8007">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8008">税の識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8008">tax identification number</span></span>

## <a name="medicare-beneficiary-identifier-mbi-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8025">メディケア受益者識別子 (MBI) カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8025">Medicare Beneficiary Identifier (MBI) card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8026">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8026">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8027">11 文字の英数字パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8027">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8028">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8028">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8029">1 ~ 9 の 1 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8029">one digit between 1 to 9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8030">S、L、O、I、B、Z を除く 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8030">one letter excluding  S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8031">S、L、O、I、B、Z を除く 1 桁または文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8031">one digit or letter excluding S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8032">1 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8032">one digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8033">オプションのハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8033">an optional Hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8034">S、L、O、I、B、Z を除く 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8034">one letter excluding  S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8035">S、L、O、I、B、Z を除く 1 桁または文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8035">one digit or letter excluding S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8036">1 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8036">one digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8037">オプションのハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8037">an optional Hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8038">S、L、O、I、B、Z を除く 2 つの文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8038">two letters excluding  S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8039">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8039">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8040">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8040">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8041">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8041">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8042">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8042">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8043">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8043">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8044">正規表現は、  `Regex_mbi_card` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8044">The regular expression  `Regex_mbi_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8045">キーワードが  `Keyword_mbi_card` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8045">A keyword from  `Keyword_mbi_card` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8046">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8046">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8047">正規表現は、  `Regex_mbi_card` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8047">The regular expression  `Regex_mbi_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Medicare Beneficiary Identifier (MBI) card -->
      <Entity id="f753a286-f5cc-47e6-a592-4be25fd02591" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_mbi_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_mbi_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_mbi_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8048">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8048">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_mbi_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8049">Keyword_mbi_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8049">Keyword_mbi_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8050">mbi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8050">mbi</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8051">mbi#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8051">mbi#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8052">medicare 受益者#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8052">medicare beneficiary #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8053">medicare 受益者識別子</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8053">medicare beneficiary identifier</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8054">medicare 受益者なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8054">medicare beneficiary no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8055">medicare 受益者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8055">medicare beneficiary number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8056">medicare 受益者#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8056">medicare beneficiary#</span></span>


## <a name="mexico-unique-population-registry-code-curp"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8057">メキシコ固有の人口レジストリ コード (CURP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8057">Mexico Unique Population Registry Code (CURP)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8058">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8058">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8059">18 文字の英数字パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8059">18 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8060">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8060">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8061">4 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8061">four letters (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8062">有効な日付を示す 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8062">six digits indicating a valid date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8063">文字 - H/h または M/m</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8063">a letter - H/h or M/m</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8064">有効なメキシコの州コードを示す 2 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8064">two letters indicating a valid Mexican state code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8065">3 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8065">three letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8066">1 文字または数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8066">one letter or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8067">1 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8067">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8068">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8068">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8069">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8069">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8070">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8070">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8071">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8071">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8072">この関数  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8072">The function  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8073">キーワードが  `Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8073">A keyword from  `Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8074">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8074">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8075">この関数  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8075">The function  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Mexico Unique Population Registry Code (CURP) -->
      <Entity id="e905ad4d-5a74-406d-bf36-b1efca798af4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_mexico_population_registry_code" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_mexico_population_registry_code" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8080">一意の母集団レジストリ コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8080">Unique Population Registry Code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8081">一意の母集団コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8081">unique population code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8084">一意の ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8084">Unique ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8087">uniqueidkey</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8087">uniqueidkey</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8089">clave única</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8089">clave única</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8091">clave 個人用 Identidad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8091">clave personal Identidad</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8093">ClaveÚnica</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8093">ClaveÚnica</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8095">clavepersonalIdentidad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8095">clavepersonalIdentidad</span></span>


## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8096">オランダの市民サービス (BSN) 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8096">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8097">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8097">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8098">オプションのスペースを含む 8 桁または 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8098">eight or nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8099">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8099">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8100">89 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8100">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8101">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8101">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8102">スペース (オプション)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8102">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8103">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8103">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8104">スペース (オプション)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8104">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8105">2 桁の 3 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8105">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8106">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8106">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8107">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8107">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8108">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8108">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8109">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8109">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8110">この関数はFunc_netherlands_bsn一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8110">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8111">このページのKeyword_netherlands_bsnが見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8111">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8112">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8112">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8123">persoonlijk nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8123">persoonlijk nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8124">persoonlijke numerieke コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8124">persoonlijke numerieke code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8126">persoonsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8126">persoonsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8127">sociaal-fiscaal nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8127">sociaal-fiscaal nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8128">ソーシャル会計番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8128">social-fiscal number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8129">sofi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8129">sofi</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8130">sofinummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8130">sofinummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8131">uniek identificatienummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8131">uniek identificatienummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8132">uniek identiteitsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8132">uniek identiteitsnummer</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8136">オランダの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8136">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8137">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8137">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8138">スペースと区切り記号のない 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8138">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8139">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8139">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8140">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8140">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8141">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8141">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8142">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8142">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8143">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8143">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8144">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8144">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8145">正規表現は、  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8145">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8146">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8146">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="6247fbea-ab80-4be5-8233-308b7c031401" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8274">オランダのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8274">Netherlands passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8275">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8275">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8276">スペースまたは区切り記号がない 9 文字または数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8276">nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8277">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8277">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8278">9 文字または数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8278">nine letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8279">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8279">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8280">該当なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8280">not applicable</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8281">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8281">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8282">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8282">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8283">正規表現は、  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8283">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8284">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8284">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8285">正規表現は `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` 、DD MMM/MMM YYYYY 形式の日付を検索します (例 - 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8285">The regular expression `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8286">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8286">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8287">正規表現は、  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8287">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8288">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8288">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61786727-bafd-45f6-94d9-888d815e228e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8306">オランダの納税者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8306">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8307">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8307">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8308">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8308">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8309">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8309">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8310">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8310">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8311">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8311">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8312">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8312">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8313">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8313">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8314">スペースまたは区切り記号のない 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8314">nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8315">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8315">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8316">9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8316">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8317">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8317">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8318">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8318">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8319">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8319">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8320">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8320">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8321">この関数  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8321">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8322">キーワードが  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8322">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8323">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8323">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8324">この関数  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8324">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8362">オランダの付加価値税番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8362">Netherlands value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8363">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8363">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8364">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8364">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8365">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8365">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8366">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8366">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8367">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8367">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8368">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8368">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8369">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8369">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8370">14 文字の英数字パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8370">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8371">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8371">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8372">14 文字の英数字パターン:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8372">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8373">N または n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8373">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8374">L または l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8374">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8375">オプションのスペース、ドット、またはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8375">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8376">9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8376">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8377">オプションのスペース、ドット、またはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8377">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8378">B または b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8378">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8379">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8379">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8380">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8380">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8381">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8381">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8382">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8382">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8383">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8383">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8384">この関数はFunc_netherlands_value_added_tax_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8384">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8385">このページのKeywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_numberが見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8385">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8386">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8386">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-8387">この関数はFunc_netherlands_value_added_tax_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-8387">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="4f320d9b-4972-41ae-b337-88d499bb1ade" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
