## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9205">ポルトガルの納税者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9205">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9206">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9206">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9207">オプションのスペースを含む 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9207">nine digits with optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9208">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9208">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9209">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9209">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9210">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9210">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9211">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9211">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9212">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9212">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9213">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9213">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9214">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9214">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9215">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9215">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9216">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9216">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9217">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9217">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9218">この関数  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9218">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9219">キーワードが  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9219">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9220">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9220">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9221">この関数  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9221">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9222">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9222">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9223">Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9223">Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9224">cpf#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9224">cpf#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9225">cpf</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9225">cpf</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9226">nif#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9226">nif#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9227">nif</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9227">nif</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9228">número de identificação fisca</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9228">número de identificação fisca</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9229">numero fiscal</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9229">numero fiscal</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9230">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9230">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9231">税の識別なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9231">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9232">税の識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9232">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9233">tax no#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9233">tax no#</span></span>

## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9246">ルーマニアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9246">Romania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9247">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9247">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9248">1 文字の後に 8 桁の数字を付け</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9248">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9249">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9249">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9250">1 文字の後に 8 桁の数字が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9250">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9251">1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない) または数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9251">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9252">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9252">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9253">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9253">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9254">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9254">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9255">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9255">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9256">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9256">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9257">正規表現は、  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9257">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9258">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9258">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Romania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="b5511ace-2fd8-4ae4-b6fc-c7c6e4689e3c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-personal-numeric-code-cnp"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9386">ルーマニアの個人数値コード (CNP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9386">Romania personal numeric code (CNP)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9387">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9387">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9388">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9388">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9389">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9389">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9390">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9390">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9391">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9391">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9392">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9392">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9393">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9393">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9394">スペースと区切り記号のない 13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9394">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9395">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9395">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9396">1 ~ 9 の 1 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9396">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9397">生年月日 (YYMMDD) を表す 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9397">six digits representing date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9398">2 桁の数字 (01 ~ 52 または 99)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9398">two digits, which can be 01-52 or 99</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9399">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9399">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9400">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9400">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9401">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9401">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9402">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9402">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9403">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9403">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9404">この関数  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9404">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9405">キーワードが  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9405">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9406">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9406">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9407">この関数  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9407">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Romania Personal Numerical Code (CNP) -->
      <Entity id="eb5fa399-fe28-4c67-8188-d63a616ed89c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9458">ルーマニアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9458">Romania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9459">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9459">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9460">スペースと区切り記号のない 8 桁または 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9460">eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9461">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9461">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9462">8 桁または 9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9462">eight or nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9463">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9463">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9464">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9464">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9465">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9465">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9466">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9466">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9467">正規表現は、  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9467">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9468">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9468">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9469">正規表現は `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` 、DD MMM/MMM YY (例- 01 FEB/FEB 10) 形式の日付を検索するか、キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9469">The regular expression `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (Example- 01 FEB/FEB 10) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9470">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9470">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9471">正規表現は、  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9471">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9472">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9472">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Romania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5d31b90c-7fe2-4a76-a14b-767b8fd19d6c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="russia-passport-number-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9490">ロシアのパスポート番号 (国内)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9490">Russia passport number domestic</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9491">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9491">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9492">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9492">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9493">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9493">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9494">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9494">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9495">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9495">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9496">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9496">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9497">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9497">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9498">10 桁の番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9498">10-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9499">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9499">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9500">10 桁の番号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9500">10-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9501">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9501">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9502">オプションのスペースまたはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9502">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9503">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9503">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9504">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9504">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9505">6 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9505">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9506">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9506">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9507">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9507">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9508">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9508">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9509">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9509">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9510">正規表現はRegex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9510">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9511">ユーザーのキーワードKeyword_Russian_Passport_Number見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9511">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number Domestic -->
      <Entity id="76ec2f5d-cedb-48e1-8070-1998794af445" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="russia-passport-number-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9528">ロシアのパスポート番号国際</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9528">Russia passport number international</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9529">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9529">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9530">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9530">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9531">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9531">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9532">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9532">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9533">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9533">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9534">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9534">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9535">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9535">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9536">9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9536">nine-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9537">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9537">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9538">9 桁の番号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9538">nine-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9539">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9539">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9540">オプションのスペースまたはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9540">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9541">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9541">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9542">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9542">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9543">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9543">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9544">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9544">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9545">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9545">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9546">正規表現はRegex_Russian_Passport_Number_International一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9546">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9547">ユーザーのキーワードKeyword_Russian_Passport_Number見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9547">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number International -->
      <Entity id="ac5f4878-75e4-4b82-af2d-02e13ea9f411" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9556">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9556">паспорт нет</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9557">паспорт ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9557">паспорт id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9559">pусский номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9559">pусский номер паспорта</span></span>

## <a name="saudi-arabia-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9564">サウジアラビアの国民 ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9564">Saudi Arabia National ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9565">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9565">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9566">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9566">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9567">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9567">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9568">10 桁の連続する数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9568">10 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9569">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9569">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9570">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9570">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9571">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9571">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9572">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9572">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9573">正規表現 Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9573">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9574">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9574">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->
<Entity id="8c5a0ba8-404a-41a3-8871-746aa21ee6c0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9575">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9575">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9577">Identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9577">Identification Card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9579">ID number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9579">ID number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9580">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9580">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span></span>


## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9581">シンガポールの国民登録 ID カード (NRIC) 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9581">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9582">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9582">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9583">9 文字と数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9583">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9584">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9584">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9585">9 文字と数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9585">nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9586">文字 "F"、"G"、"S"、または "T" (大文字と小文字を区別しない)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9586">the letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9587">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9587">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9588">英字チェックの数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9588">an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9589">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9589">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9590">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9590">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9591">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9591">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9592">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9592">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9593">正規表現は、Regex_singapore_nric一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9593">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9594">このページのKeyword_singapore_nric見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9594">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9595">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9595">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9596">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9596">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9597">正規表現は、Regex_singapore_nric一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9597">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9598">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9598">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9609">スロバキアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9609">Slovakia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9610">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9610">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9611">1 文字の後に 7 桁の数字を付け</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9611">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9612">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9612">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9613">1 文字の後に 7 桁の数字を付け</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9613">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9614">1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない) または数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9614">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9615">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9615">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9616">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9616">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9617">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9617">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9618">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9618">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9619">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9619">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9620">正規表現は、  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9620">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9621">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9621">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="14240c22-b6de-4ce5-a90b-137f74252513" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-personal-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9747">スロバキアの個人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9747">Slovakia personal number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9748">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9748">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9749">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9749">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9750">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9750">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9751">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9751">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9752">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9752">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9753">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9753">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9754">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9754">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9755">オプションの円記号を含む 9 桁または 10 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9755">nine or 10 digits containing optional backslash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9756">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9756">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9757">生年月日を表す 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9757">six digits representing date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9758">省略可能なスラッシュ (/)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9758">optional slash (/)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9759">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9759">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9760">オプションのチェックディジット 1 つ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9760">one optional check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9761">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9761">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9762">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9762">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9763">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9763">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9764">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9764">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9765">この関数  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9765">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9766">キーワードが  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9766">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9767">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9767">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9768">この関数  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9768">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Personal Number -->
      <Entity id="951c26b7-3b35-4f73-924b-15dd599cb9ab" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="slovakia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9815">スロバキアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9815">Slovakia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9816">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9816">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9817">1 桁または文字の後にスペースまたは区切り記号を付けない 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9817">one digit or letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9818">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9818">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9819">1 桁または文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない) の後に 7 桁の数字が続く</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9819">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9820">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9820">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9821">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9821">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9822">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9822">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9823">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9823">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9824">正規表現は、  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9824">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9825">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9825">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9826">正規表現が `Regex_eu_passport_date1` DD.MM.YYYYY 形式の日付を検索するか、キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9826">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9827">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9827">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9828">正規表現は、  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9828">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9829">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9829">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="238e1f08-d80e-4793-af33-9b57918335b7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9851">スロベニアの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9851">Slovenia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9852">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9852">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9853">スペースと区切り記号のない 9 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9853">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9854">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9854">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9855">9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9855">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9856">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9856">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9857">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9857">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9858">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9858">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9859">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9859">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9860">正規表現は、  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9860">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9861">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9861">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5bc089a-f2ee-433d-a6b1-5c253051d6f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-unique-master-citizen-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9988">スロベニアの一意のマスター市民番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9988">Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9989">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9989">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9990">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9990">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9991">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9991">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9992">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9992">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9993">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9993">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9994">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9994">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9995">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9995">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9996">スペースまたは区切り記号のない 13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9996">13 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9997">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9997">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9998">指定したパターンの 13 桁:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9998">13 digits in the specified pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-9999">"LLL" が生年月日の最後の 3 桁に対応する生年月日 (DDMMLLL) に対応する 7 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-9999">seven digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMLLL) where "LLL" corresponds to the last three digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10000">出生領域 "50" に対応する 2 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10000">two digits that correspond to the area of birth "50"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10001">同じ日に生まれた人の性別とシリアル番号の組み合わせに対応する 3 桁の数字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10001">three digits that correspond to a combination of gender and serial number for persons born on the same day.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10002">男性は 000 ~499、女性は 500 ~999 です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10002">000-499 for male and 500-999 for female.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10003">1 つのチェックディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10003">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10004">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10004">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10005">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10005">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10006">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10006">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10007">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10007">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10008">この関数  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10008">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10009">キーワードが  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10009">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10010">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10010">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10011">この関数  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10011">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number -->
      <Entity id="68948b27-803d-41e4-adf1-13e05eb541bb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10039">スロベニアのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10039">Slovenia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10040">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10040">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10041">2 文字の後に 7 桁の数字が続き、スペースまたは区切り記号は使用されません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10041">two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10042">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10042">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10043">2 文字の後に 7 桁の数字が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10043">two letters followed by seven digits:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10044">文字 "P"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10044">the letter "P"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10045">大文字 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10045">one uppercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10046">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10046">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10047">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10047">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10048">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10048">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10049">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10049">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10050">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10050">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10051">正規表現は、  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10051">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10052">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10052">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10053">正規表現が `Regex_eu_passport_date1` DD.MM.YYYYY 形式の日付を検索するか、キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10053">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10054">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10054">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10055">正規表現は、  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10055">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10056">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10056">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="235b7976-7bbe-4df5-bb40-08678e749d1a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10070">številka potnega lista</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10070">številka potnega lista</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10071">potek veljavnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10071">potek veljavnosti</span></span>

## <a name="slovenia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10079">スロベニアの納税者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10079">Slovenia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10080">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10080">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10081">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10081">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10082">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10082">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10083">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10083">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10084">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10084">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10085">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10085">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10086">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10086">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10087">スペースまたは区切り記号がない 8 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10087">eight digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10088">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10088">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10089">1 ~ 9 の 1 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10089">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10090">6 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10090">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10091">1 つのチェックディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10091">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10092">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10092">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10093">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10093">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10094">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10094">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10095">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10095">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10096">この関数  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10096">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10097">キーワードが  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10097">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10098">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10098">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10099">この関数  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10099">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="e47b071e-c352-4d70-8241-8c215ad65505" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10120">tin id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10120">tin id</span></span>

## <a name="south-africa-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10123">南アフリカの ID 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10123">South Africa identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10124">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10124">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10125">省略可能なスペースを含む 13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10125">13 digits that may contain spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10126">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10126">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10127">13 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10127">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10128">YYMMDD 形式の 6 桁の数字 (生年月日)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10128">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10129">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10129">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10130">1 桁の市民権インジケーター</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10130">a single-digit citizenship indicator</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10131">数字 "8" または "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10131">the digit "8" or "9"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10132">1 桁(チェックサム桁)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10132">one digit, which is a checksum digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10133">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10133">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10134">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10134">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10135">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10135">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10136">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10136">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10137">この関数Func_south_africa_identification_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10137">The function Func_south_africa_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10138">このページのKeyword_south_africa_identification_numberが見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10138">A keyword from Keyword_south_africa_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10139">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10139">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Africa Identification Number -->
<Entity id="e2adf7cb-8ea6-4048-a2ed-d89eb65f2780" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_africa_identification_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_africa_identification_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10140">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10140">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_south_africa_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10141">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10141">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10142">Identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10142">Identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10143">ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10143">ID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10144">ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10144">Identification</span></span>

## <a name="south-korea-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10145">韓国居住者登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10145">South Korea resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10146">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10146">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10147">ハイフンを 1 つ含む 13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10147">13 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10148">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10148">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10149">13 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10149">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10150">YYMMDD 形式の 6 桁の数字 (生年月日)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10150">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10151">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10151">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10152">世紀と性別によって決まる 1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10152">one digit determined by the century and gender</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10153">4 桁の出生地域コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10153">four-digit region-of-birth code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10154">前の番号が同一のユーザーを区別するために使用される 1 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10154">one digit used to differentiate people for whom the preceding numbers are identical</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10155">チェックの数字を指定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10155">a check digit.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10156">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10156">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10157">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10157">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10158">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10158">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10159">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10159">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10160">この関数はFunc_south_korea_resident_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10160">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10161">ユーザーのキーワードKeyword_south_korea_resident_number見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10161">A keyword from Keyword_south_korea_resident_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10162">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10162">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10163">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10163">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10164">この関数はFunc_south_korea_resident_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10164">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10165">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10165">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Korea Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="5b802e18-ba80-44c4-bc83-bf2ad36ae36a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10166">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10166">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_south_korea_resident_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10167">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10167">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10169">Citizen's Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10169">Citizen's Registration Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10170">Jumin deungnok beonho</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10170">Jumin deungnok beonho</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10171">RRN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10171">RRN</span></span>

## <a name="spain-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10173">スペインの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10173">Spain driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10174">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10174">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10175">8 桁の数字の後に 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10175">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10176">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10176">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10177">8 桁の数字の後に 1 文字が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10177">eight digits followed by one character:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10178">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10178">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10179">1 桁または 1 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10179">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10180">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10180">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10181">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10181">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10182">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10182">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10183">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10183">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10184">パターンに  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 一 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 致するコンテンツを関数または検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10184">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10185">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10185">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10186">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10186">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10187">パターンに  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 一 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 致するコンテンツを関数または検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10187">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Spain Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5a82922-b501-4f40-8868-341321146aa2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-dni"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10321">スペイン DNI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10321">Spain DNI</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10322">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10322">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10323">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10323">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10324">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10324">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10325">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10325">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10326">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10326">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10327">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10327">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10328">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10328">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10329">8 桁の数字の後に 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10329">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10330">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10330">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10331">7 桁の数字の後に 1 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10331">seven digits followed by one character</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10332">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10332">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10333">オプションのスペースまたはハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10333">An optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10334">1 つのチェック文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10334">one check letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10335">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10335">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10336">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10336">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10337">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10337">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10338">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10338">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10339">パターンに  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 一 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 致するコンテンツを関数または検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10339">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10340">キーワードが  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10340">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10341">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10341">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10342">パターンに  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 一 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 致するコンテンツを関数または検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10342">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- Spain DNI -->
      <Entity id="8e6251b9-47b4-40e8-a42b-0f80876be192" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
