## <a name="spain-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10366">スペインのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10366">Spain passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10367">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10367">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10368">8 文字または 9 文字の文字と数字の組み合わせで、スペースや区切り記号はありません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10368">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10369">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10369">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10370">文字と数字の 8 文字または 9 文字の組み合わせ。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10370">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10371">2 桁の数字または文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10371">two digits or letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10372">1 桁または 1 文字 (オプション)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10372">one digit or letter (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10373">6 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10373">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10374">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10374">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10375">該当しない</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10375">Not applicable</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10376">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10376">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10377">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10377">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10378">正規表現は、  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10378">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10379">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10379">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10380">正規表現が `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` DD-MM-YYYY 形式の日付を検索するか、キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10380">The regular expression `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD-MM-YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10381">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10381">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10382">正規表現は、  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10382">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10383">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10383">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Spain Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d17a57de-9fa5-4e9f-85d3-85c26d89686e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10412">スペインの社会保障番号 (SSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10412">Spain social security number (SSN)</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10413">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10413">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10414">11 ～ 12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10414">11-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10415">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10415">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10416">11 ~ 12 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10416">11-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10417">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10417">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10418">スラッシュ (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10418">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10419">7 桁から 8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10419">seven to eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10420">スラッシュ (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10420">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10421">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10421">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10422">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10422">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10423">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10423">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10424">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10424">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10425">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10425">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10426">関数 Func_spanish_social_security_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10426">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10427">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10427">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- - <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10428">キーワードが  `Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10428">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10429">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10429">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10430">関数 Func_spanish_social_security_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10430">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10431">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10431">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Spain SSN -->
    <Entity id="5df987c0-8eae-4bce-ace7-b316347f3070" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true" >
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10432">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10432">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_spain_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10433">Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10433">Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10434">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10434">ssn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10435">ssn#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10435">ssn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10436">socialsecurityno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10436">socialsecurityno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10437">社会保障なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10437">social security no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10438">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10438">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10439">número de la seguridad social</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10439">número de la seguridad social</span></span>

## <a name="spain-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10440">スペインの納税者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10440">Spain tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10441">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10441">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10442">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10442">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10443">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10443">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10444">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10444">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10445">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10445">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10446">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10446">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10447">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10447">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10448">指定したパターンの 7 桁または 8 桁の数字と 1 文字または 2 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10448">seven or eight digits and one or two letters in the specified pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10449">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10449">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10450">スペインの国民 ID カードを持つスペインの自然人:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10450">Spanish Natural Persons with a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10451">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10451">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10452">大文字 1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10452">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10453">スペイン国民 ID カードのない非居住者のスペイン語</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10453">Non-resident Spaniards without a Spain National Identity Card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10454">1 つの大文字 "L" (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10454">one uppercase letter "L" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10455">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10455">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10456">大文字 1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10456">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10457">スペイン国民 ID カードのない 14 歳未満のスペイン居住者:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10457">Resident Spaniards under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10458">1 つの大文字 "K" (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10458">one uppercase letter "K" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10459">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10459">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10460">大文字 1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10460">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10461">外国人の身分証明番号を持つ外国人</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10461">Foreigners with a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10462">"X"、"Y"、または "Z" である 1 つの大文字 (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10462">one uppercase letter that is "X", "Y", or "Z" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10463">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10463">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10464">大文字 1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10464">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10465">外国人の身分証明番号を持つ外国人</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10465">Foreigners without a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10466">"M" の 1 つの大文字 (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10466">one uppercase letter that is "M" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10467">7 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10467">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10468">大文字 1 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10468">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10469">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10469">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10470">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10470">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10471">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10471">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10472">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10472">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10473">パターンに  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` 一 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 致するコンテンツを関数または検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10473">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10474">キーワードが  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10474">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10475">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10475">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10476">パターンに  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` 一 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 致するコンテンツを関数または検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10476">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Spain Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="10f0d113-b0e1-47dc-872a-a4f45b9376a3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sql-server-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10507">SQL Server接続文字列</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10507">SQL Server connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10508">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10508">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10509">文字列 "User Id"、"User ID"、"uid"、または "UserId" の後に、以下のパターンで概説されている文字と文字列が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10509">The string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10510">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10510">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10511">文字列 "User Id"、"User ID"、"uid"、または "UserId"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10511">the string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10512">1 ~ 200 文字の小文字または大文字、数字、記号、特殊文字、またはスペースの任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10512">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10513">"pwd" の前に小文字が付かされていない文字列 "Password" または "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10513">the string "Password" or "pwd" where "pwd" isn't preceded by a lowercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10514">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10514">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10515">ドル記号 ($)、パーセント記号 (%)、記号 (> より大きい)、記号 (@)、引用符 (")、セミコロン (;)、左中かっこ([)、または左かっこ ({) 以外の文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10515">any character that isn't a dollar sign ($), percent symbol (%), greater than symbol (>), at symbol (@), quotation mark ("), semicolon (;), left brace([), or left bracket ({)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10516">セミコロンではない 7 ~ 128 文字の任意の組み合わせ (;)、スラッシュ (/)、または引用符 (")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10516">any combination of 7-128 characters that are not a semicolon (;), forward slash (/), or quotation mark (")</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10517">セミコロン (;)または引用符 (")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10517">a semicolon (;) or quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10518">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10518">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10519">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10519">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10520">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10520">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10521">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10521">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10522">正規表現は、CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10522">The regular expression CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10523">ユーザーからのCEP_GlobalFilterが見つかりません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10523">A keyword from CEP_GlobalFilter isn't found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10524">パターンに一CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder一致するコンテンツが見当たらない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10524">The regular expression CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10525">パターンに一CEP_CommonExampleKeywords一致するコンテンツが見当たらない正規表現。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10525">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```sql
<!---SQL Server Connection String>
<Entity id="e76b6205-d3cb-46f2-bd63-c90153f2f97d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_GlobalFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10526">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10526">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_globalfilter"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10527">CEP_GlobalFilter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10527">CEP_GlobalFilter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10528">一部のパスワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10528">some-password</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10529">somepassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10529">somepassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10530">secretPassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10530">secretPassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10531">サンプル</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10531">sample</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_passwordplaceholder"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10532">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10532">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10533">この機密情報の種類は、キーワード リストではなく正規表現を使用して、これらのキーワードを識別します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10533">This sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10534">パスワードまたは pwd の後に 0 ~ 2 スペース、等号 (=)、0 ~ 2 スペース、およびアスタリスク (\*) -OR- が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10534">Password or pwd followed by 0-2 spaces, an equal sign (=), 0-2 spaces, and an asterisk (\*) -OR-</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10535">パスワードまたは pwd の後に次の情報が表示されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10535">Password or pwd followed by:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10536">等号 (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10536">Equal sign (=)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10537">シンボル未満 (<)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10537">Less than symbol (<)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10538">大文字または小文字、数字、アスタリスク (\*)、ハイフン (-)、下線 (_)、または空白文字である 1 ~ 200 文字の任意の組み合わせ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10538">Any combination of 1-200 characters that are upper- or lowercase letters, digits, an asterisk (\*), hyphen (-), underline (_), or whitespace character</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10539">記号より大きい (>)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10539">Greater than symbol (>)</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_commonexamplekeywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10540">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10540">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10541">この機密情報の種類は、キーワード リストではなく正規表現を使用して、これらのキーワードを識別します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10541">This sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10553">スウェーデンの運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10553">Sweden driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10554">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10554">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10555">ハイフンを 1 つ含む 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10555">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10556">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10556">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10557">ハイフンを含む 10 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10557">10 digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10558">6 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10558">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10559">ハイフン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10559">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10560">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10560">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10561">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10561">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10562">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10562">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10563">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10563">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10564">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10564">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10565">正規表現は、  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10565">The regular expression  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10566">キーワードが見  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10566">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Sweden Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="70088720-90dd-47f5-805e-5525f3567391" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10699">スウェーデンの国民 ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10699">Sweden national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10700">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10700">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10701">10 桁または 12 桁の数字とオプションの区切り記号 1 つ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10701">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10702">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10702">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10703">10 桁または 12 桁の数字と省略可能な区切り記号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10703">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10704">2 桁 (オプション)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10704">two digits (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10705">YYMMDD という日付形式の 6 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10705">Six digits in date format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10706">"-" または "+" の区切り記号 (省略可能)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10706">delimiter of "-" or "+" (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10707">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10707">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10708">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10708">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10709">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10709">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10710">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10710">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10711">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10711">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10712">この関数 `Func_swedish_national_identifier` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10712">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10713">キーワードが `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10713">A keyword from `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10714">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10714">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10715">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10715">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10716">この関数 `Func_swedish_national_identifier` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10716">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10717">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10717">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden National ID -->
    <Entity id="f69aaf40-79be-4fac-8f05-fd1910d272c8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10736">スウェーデンのパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10736">Sweden passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10737">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10737">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10738">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10738">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10739">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10739">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10740">8 桁の連続する数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10740">eight consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10741">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10741">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10742">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10742">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10743">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10743">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10744">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10744">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10745">正規表現は、Regex_sweden_passport_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10745">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10746">キーワードが見 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keyword_sweden_passport` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10746">a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_sweden_passport` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10747">正規表現は `Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date` 、DD MMM/MMM YY (01 JAN/JAN 12) 形式の日付を検索するか、キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10747">the regular expression `Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date` finds a date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (01 JAN/JAN 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10748">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10748">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10749">正規表現は、Regex_sweden_passport_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10749">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10750">キーワードが見 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keyword_sweden_passport` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10750">a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_sweden_passport` is found.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="ba4e7456-55a9-4d89-9140-c33673553526" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10786">スウェーデンの納税者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10786">Sweden tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10787">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10787">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10788">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10788">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10789">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10789">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10790">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10790">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10791">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10791">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10792">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10792">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10793">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10793">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10794">10 桁の数字と指定したパターンの記号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10794">10 digits and a symbol in the specified pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10795">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10795">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10796">10 桁の数字と記号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10796">10 digits and a symbol:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10797">生年月日に対応する 6 桁の数字 (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10797">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10798">プラス記号またはマイナス記号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10798">a plus sign or minus sign</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10799">識別番号を一意にする 3 桁の数字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10799">three digits that make the identification number unique where:</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10800">1990 年以前に発行された番号の場合、7 桁目と 8 桁目は出生国または外国生まれの人々を識別します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10800">for numbers issued before 1990, the seventh and eighth digit identify the county of birth or foreign-born people</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10801">9 番目の位置の数字は、性別を男性または女性の場合は奇数で示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10801">the digit in the ninth position indicates gender by either odd for male or even for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10802">1 つのチェックディジット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10802">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10803">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10803">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10804">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10804">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10805">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10805">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10806">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10806">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10807">この関数  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10807">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10808">キーワードが  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10808">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10809">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10809">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10810">この関数  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10810">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Sweden Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="139acba0-a5bc-4fbb-876d-f7a493ae8a40" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="swift-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10836">SWIFT コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10836">SWIFT code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10837">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10837">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10838">4 文字の後に 5 ~ 31 文字または数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10838">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10839">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10839">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10840">4 文字の後に 5 ~ 31 文字または数字が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10840">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10841">4 文字の銀行コード (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10841">four-letter bank code (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10842">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10842">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10843">4 ～ 28 個の文字または数字 (基本的銀行口座番号 (BBAN))</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10843">4-28 letters or digits (the Basic Bank Account Number (BBAN))</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10844">オプションのスペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10844">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10845">1 ~ 3 文字または数字 (BBAN の残りの部分)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10845">one to three letters or digits (remainder of the BBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10846">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10846">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10847">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10847">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10848">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10848">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10849">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10849">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10850">正規表現 Regex_swift がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10850">The regular expression Regex_swift finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10851">Keyword_swift のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10851">A keyword from Keyword_swift is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="cb2ab58c-9cb8-4c81-baf8-a4e106791df4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_swift" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_swift" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10883">BIC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10883">BIC 番号</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10885">金融機関識別コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10885">金融機関識別コード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10886">金融機関コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10886">金融機関コード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10887">銀行コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10887">銀行コード</span></span>

## <a name="switzerland-ssn-ahv-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10888">スイス SSN AHV 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10888">Switzerland SSN AHV number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10889">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10889">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10890">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10890">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10891">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10891">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10892">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10892">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10893">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10893">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10894">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10894">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10895">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10895">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10896">13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10896">13-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10897">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10897">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10898">13 桁の番号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10898">13-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10899">3 桁の数字 - 756</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10899">three digits - 756</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10900">オプションのドット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10900">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10901">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10901">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10902">オプションのドット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10902">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10903">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10903">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10904">オプションのドット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10904">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10905">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10905">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10906">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10906">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10907">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10907">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10908">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10908">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10909">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10909">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10910">この関数はFunc_swiss_social_security_number_ahv一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10910">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10911">ユーザーのキーワードKeywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10911">A keyword from Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10912">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10912">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10913">この関数はFunc_swiss_social_security_number_ahv一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10913">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Swiss SSN AHV Number -->
      <Entity id="277cfa4b-6eaa-4a1b-9492-099dec849971" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10914">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10914">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_swiss_ssn_ahv_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10915">Keyword_swiss_ssn_AHV_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10915">Keyword_swiss_ssn_AHV_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10918">pid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10918">pid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10919">保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10919">insurance number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10920">personalidno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10920">personalidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10921">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10921">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10922">個人用 ID 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10922">personal id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10923">個人識別番号。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10923">personal identification no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10924">insuranceno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10924">insuranceno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10925">uniqueidno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10925">uniqueidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10926">一意の ID いいえ。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10926">unique identification no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10927">avs 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10927">avs number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10928">個人 ID no versicherungsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10928">personal identity no versicherungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10929">identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10929">identifikationsnummer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10931">sozialversicherungsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10931">sozialversicherungsnummer</span></span>
