- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10933">numéro de sécurité sociale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10933">numéro de sécurité sociale</span></span>


## <a name="taiwan-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10934">台湾の国民識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10934">Taiwan national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10935">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10935">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10936">1 文字 (英語) の後に 9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10936">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10937">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10937">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10938">1 文字 (英語) の後に 9 桁の数字が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10938">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10939">1 文字 (英語、大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10939">one letter (in English, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10940">数字 "1" または "2"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10940">the digit "1" or "2"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10941">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10941">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10942">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10942">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10943">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10943">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10944">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10944">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10945">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10945">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10946">関数 Func_taiwanese_national_id がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10946">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10947">Keyword_taiwanese_national_id のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10947">A keyword from Keyword_taiwanese_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10948">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10948">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10949">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10949">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10950">関数 Func_taiwanese_national_id がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10950">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10951">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10951">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwanese National ID -->
<Entity id="4C7BFC34-8DD1-421D-8FB7-6C6182C2AF03" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwanese_national_id" />
      </Pattern>
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
         <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
       </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10952">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10952">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10953">Keyword_taiwan_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10953">Keyword_taiwan_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10954">身份證字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10954">身份證字號</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10955">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10955">身份證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10956">身份證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10956">身份證號碼</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10957">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10957">身份證號</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10958">身分證字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10958">身分證字號</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10959">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10959">身分證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10960">身分證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10960">身分證號碼</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10961">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10961">身份證號</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10962">身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10962">身分證統一編號</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10963">國民身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10963">國民身分證統一編號</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10964">簽名</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10964">簽名</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10965">蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10965">蓋章</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10966">簽名或蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10966">簽名或蓋章</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10967">簽章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10967">簽章</span></span>

## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10968">台湾のパスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10968">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10969">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10969">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10970">生体認証パスポート番号: 9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10970">biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10971">生体認証以外のパスポート番号: 9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10971">non-biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10972">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10972">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10973">生体認証パスポート番号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10973">biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10974">文字 "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10974">the character "3"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10975">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10975">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10976">生体認証以外のパスポート番号:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10976">non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10977">9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10977">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10978">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10978">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10979">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10979">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10980">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10980">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10981">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10981">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10982">正規表現は、Regex_taiwan_passport一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10982">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10983">ユーザーからのキーワードKeyword_taiwan_passport見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10983">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10984">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10984">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10985">Keyword_taiwan_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10985">Keyword_taiwan_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10986">ROC passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10986">ROC passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10987">Passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10987">Passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10988">Passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10988">Passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10989">Passport Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10989">Passport Num</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10990">Passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10990">Passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10991">护照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10991">护照</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10992">中華民國護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10992">中華民國護照</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10993">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10993">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span></span>

## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10994">台湾在住証明書 (ARC/TARC) 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10994">Taiwan-resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10995">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10995">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10996">10 桁の文字と数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10996">10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10997">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10997">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10998">10 桁の文字と数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10998">10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-10999">2 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-10999">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11000">8 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11000">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11001">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11001">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11002">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11002">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11003">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11003">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11004">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11004">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11005">正規表現は、Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11005">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11006">このページのKeyword_taiwan_resident_certificate見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11006">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11007">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11007">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11008">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11008">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11009">Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11009">Resident Certificate</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11010">Resident Cert</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11010">Resident Cert</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11011">Resident Cert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11011">Resident Cert.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11012">Identification card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11012">Identification card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11013">Alien Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11013">Alien Resident Certificate</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11014">ARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11014">ARC</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11015">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11015">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11016">TARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11016">TARC</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11017">居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11017">居留證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11018">外僑居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11018">外僑居留證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11019">台灣地區居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11019">台灣地區居留證</span></span>

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11020">タイの人口識別コード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11020">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11021">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11021">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11022">13 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11022">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11023">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11023">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11024">13 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11024">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11025">1 桁目が 0 または 9 ではない</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11025">first digit isn't zero or nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11026">12 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11026">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11027">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11027">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11028">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11028">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11029">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11029">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11030">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11030">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11031">この関数はFunc_Thai_Citizen_Id一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11031">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11032">ユーザーのキーワードKeyword_Thai_Citizen_Id見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11032">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11033">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11033">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11034">この関数はFunc_Thai_Citizen_Id一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11034">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11035">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11035">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_thai_citizen_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11036">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11036">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11037">ID 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11037">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11038">ID 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11038">Identification Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11039">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11039">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11040">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11040">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11041">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11041">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11042">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11042">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>

## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11043">トルコの国民識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11043">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11044">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11044">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11045">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11045">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11046">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11046">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11047">11 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11047">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11048">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11048">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11049">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11049">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11050">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11050">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11051">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11051">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11052">この関数はFunc_Turkish_National_Id一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11052">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11053">ユーザーからのキーワードKeyword_Turkish_National_Id見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11053">A keyword from Keyword_Turkish_National_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11054">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11054">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11055">この関数はFunc_Turkish_National_Id一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11055">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11056">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11056">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_turkish_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11057">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11057">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11058">TC Kimlik No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11058">TC Kimlik No</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11059">TC Kimlik numarası</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11059">TC Kimlik numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11060">Vatandaşlık numarası</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11060">Vatandaşlık numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11061">Vatandaşlık no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11061">Vatandaşlık no</span></span>

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11062">英国</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11062">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11063">運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11063">driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11064">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11064">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11065">指定の形式で組み合わせた 18 桁の文字と数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11065">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11066">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11066">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11067">18 個の文字と数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11067">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11068">5 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません) または文字の代りとして数字 "9" を指定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11068">Five letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11069">1 桁の数字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11069">One digit.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11070">生年月日の日付形式 MMDDY の 5 桁。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11070">Five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11071">ドライバーが女性の場合、7 番目の文字は 50 ずつ増加します。exampe の場合は、01 ~ 12 ではなく 51 ~ 62 です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11071">The seventh character is incremented by 50 if driver is female; for exampe, 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11072">2 文字 (大文字と小文字は区別されません) または文字の代りとして"9" という数字を指定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11072">Two letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11073">5 桁の数字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11073">Five digits.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11074">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11074">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11075">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11075">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11076">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11076">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11077">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11077">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11078">この関数 `Func_uk_drivers_license` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11078">The function `Func_uk_drivers_license` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11079">キーワードが `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11079">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11080">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11080">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11081">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11081">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11082">この関数 `Func_uk_drivers_license` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11082">The function `Func_uk_drivers_license` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11083">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11083">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true" >
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11204">英国</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11204">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11205">選挙ロール番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11205">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11206">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11206">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11207">2 文字の後に 1 ~ 4 桁の数字が続く</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11207">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11208">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11208">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11209">2 文字 (大文字と小文字を区別しない) の後に 1 ~ 4 の数字が続く</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11209">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11210">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11210">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11211">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11211">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11212">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11212">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11213">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11213">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11214">正規表現 Regex_uk_electoral がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11214">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11215">Keyword_uk_electoral のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11215">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11216">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11216">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_electoral"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11217">Keyword_uk_electoral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11217">Keyword_uk_electoral</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11218">council nomination</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11218">council nomination</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11219">nomination form</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11219">nomination form</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11220">electoral register</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11220">electoral register</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11221">electoral roll</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11221">electoral roll</span></span>


## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11222">英国</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11222">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11223">国民保健サービス番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11223">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11224">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11224">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11225">スペースで区切られた 10 ～ 17 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11225">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11226">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11226">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11227">10 ～ 17 桁の数字:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11227">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11228">3 桁または 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11228">either 3 or 10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11229">スペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11229">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11230">3 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11230">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11231">スペース</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11231">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11232">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11232">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11233">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11233">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11234">はい</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11234">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11235">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11235">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11236">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11236">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11237">関数 Func_uk_nhs_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11237">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11238">次のいずれかの条件に該当する:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11238">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11239">Keyword_uk_nhs_number のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11239">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11240">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11240">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11241">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11241">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11242">チェックサムが渡される。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11242">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11243">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11243">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11245">national health service</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11245">national health service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11247">health services authority</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11247">health services authority</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11248">health authority</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11248">health authority</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number1"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11249">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11249">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11250">patient id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11250">patient id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11251">patient identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11251">patient identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11252">patient no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11252">patient no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11253">patient number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11253">patient number</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11254">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11254">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11255">GP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11255">GP</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11256">DOB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11256">DOB</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11257">D.O.B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11257">D.O.B</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11258">Date of Birth</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11258">Date of Birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11259">Birth Date</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11259">Birth Date</span></span>

## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11260">英国</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11260">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11261">国民保険番号 (NINO)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11261">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11262">この機密情報の種類エンティティは、EU の国民識別番号の機密情報の種類に含まれています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11262">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11263">また、スタンドアロンの機密情報の種類エンティティとして利用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11263">It's also available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11264">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11264">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11265">スペースまたはダッシュで区切られた 7 文字または 9 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11265">seven characters or nine characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11266">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11266">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11267">次の 2 つのパターンを使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11267">two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11268">2 つの文字 (有効な NINOs は、このプレフィックスで特定の文字のみを使用します。このパターンは検証しますが、大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11268">two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11269">6 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11269">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11270">'A'、'B'、'C'、または 'D' のどちらか (プレフィックスと同様に、サフィックスでは特定の文字のみを使用できます。大文字と小文字は区別されません)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11270">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11271">または</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11271">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11272">2 文字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11272">two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11273">スペースまたはダッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11273">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11274">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11274">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11275">スペースまたはダッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11275">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11276">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11276">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11277">スペースまたはダッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11277">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11278">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11278">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11279">スペースまたはダッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11279">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11280">'A'、'B'、'C'、または 'D'</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11280">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D'</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11281">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11281">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11282">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11282">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11283">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11283">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11284">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11284">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11285">関数 Func_uk_nino がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11285">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11286">Keyword_uk_nino のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11286">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11287">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11287">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11288">関数 Func_uk_nino がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11288">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. NINO -->
    <Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-unique-taxpayer-reference-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11310">英国</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11310">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11311">一意の納税者参照番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11311">Unique Taxpayer Reference Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11312">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11312">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11313">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11313">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11314">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11314">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11315">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11315">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11316">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11316">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11317">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11317">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11318">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11318">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11319">スペースと区切り記号のない 10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11319">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>


### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11320">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11320">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11321">10 桁の数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11321">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11322">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11322">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11323">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11323">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11324">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11324">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11325">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11325">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11326">この関数  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` は、パターンに一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11326">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11327">キーワードが  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` 見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11327">A keyword from  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- U.K. Unique Taxpayer Reference Number -->
      <Entity id="ad4a8116-0db8-439a-b545-6d967642f0ec" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11347">米国の銀行口座番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11347">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11348">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11348">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11349">6 ~ 17 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11349">6-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11350">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11350">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11351">6 ~ 17 桁の連続する数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11351">6-17 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11352">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11352">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11353">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11353">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11354">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11354">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11355">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11355">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11356">正規表現は、Regex_usa_bank_account_number一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11356">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11357">Keyword_usa_Bank_Account のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11357">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11387">米国の運転免許証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11387">U.S. driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11388">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11388">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11389">州に応じて異なる</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11389">Depends on the state</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11390">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11390">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11391">状態によって異なります 。たとえば、ニューヨーク:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11391">depends on the state - for example, New York:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11392">ddd ddd ddd のように書式設定された 9 桁の数字が一致します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11392">nine digits formatted like ddd ddd ddd will match.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11393">dddddddddd のような 9 桁の数字は一致しません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11393">nine digits like ddddddddd will not match.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11394">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11394">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11395">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11395">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11396">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11396">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11397">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11397">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11398">関数 Func_new_york_drivers_license_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11398">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11399">Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11399">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11400">ユーザーのキーワードKeyword_us_drivers_license見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11400">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11401">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11401">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11402">関数 Func_new_york_drivers_license_number がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11402">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11403">Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11403">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11404">Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11404">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11405">Keyword_us_drivers_license のキーワードを検出しなかった。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11405">No keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="dfeb356f-61cd-459e-bf0f-7c6d28b458c6 patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_us_drivers_license"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11424">Keyword_us_drivers_license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11424">Keyword_us_drivers_license</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11425">DriverLic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11425">DriverLic</span></span>

## <a name="us-individual-taxpayer-identification-number-itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11503">米国の個人納税者 ID 番号 (ITIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11503">U.S. individual taxpayer identification number (ITIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11504">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11504">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11505">"9" で始まる 9 桁の数字で、4 桁目として "7" または "8" を含み、必要に応じてスペースまたはダッシュで書式設定されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11505">nine digits that start with a "9" and contain a "7" or "8" as the fourth digit, optionally formatted with spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11506">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11506">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11507">書式設定:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11507">formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11508">数字 "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11508">the digit "9"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11509">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11509">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11510">スペースまたはダッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11510">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11511">"7" または "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11511">a "7" or "8"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11512">数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11512">a digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11513">スペース、またはダッシュ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11513">a space, or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11514">4 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11514">four digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11515">unformatted:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11515">unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11516">数字 "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11516">the digit "9"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11517">2 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11517">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11518">"7" または "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11518">a "7" or "8"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11519">5 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11519">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11520">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11520">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11521">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11521">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11522">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11522">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11523">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11523">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11524">関数 Func_formatted_itin がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11524">The function Func_formatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11525">Keyword_itin のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11525">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11526">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11526">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11527">関数 Func_unformatted_itin がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11527">The function Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11528">Keyword_itin のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11528">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11529">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11529">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11530">この関数はFunc_formatted_itin一Func_unformatted_itin一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11530">The function Func_formatted_itin or Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN) -->
    <Entity id="e55e2a32-f92d-4985-a35d-a0b269eb687b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="us-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11545">米国の社会保障番号 (SSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11545">U.S. social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11546">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11546">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11547">9 桁の数字 (書式付きまたは書式設定されていないパターンの場合があります)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11547">nine digits, which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11548">2011 年半ばより前に発行された場合、SSN には強力な書式が設定されています。この場合、数値の特定の部分が有効な範囲内に入る必要があります (チェックサムはありません)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11548">If issued before mid-2011, an SSN has strong formatting where certain parts of the number must fall within certain ranges to be valid (but there's no checksum).</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11549">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11549">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11550">4 つの関数は、4 つの異なるパターンで SSN を探します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11550">four functions look for SSNs in four different patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11551">Func_ssn は、2011 年以前の厳密な書式の SSN を検索します。これはダッシュまたはスペース (ddd-dd-dddd または ddd dd dddd) の形式になっています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11551">Func_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11552">Func_unformatted_ssn は、2011 年以前の厳密な書式の SSN を検索します。これは 9 桁の連続した数字 (ddddddddd) の形式になっています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11552">Func_unformatted_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11553">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn は、2011 年以降の SSN を検索します。これはダッシュまたはスペース (ddd-dd-dddd または ddd dd dddd) の形式になっています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11553">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11554">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn は、2011 年以降の SSN を検索します。これは 9 桁の連続した数字 (ddddddddd) の形式になっています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11554">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11555">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11555">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11556">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11556">No</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11557">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11557">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11558">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11558">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11559">関数 Func_ssn がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11559">The function Func_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11560">Keyword_ssn のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11560">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11561">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11561">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11562">この関数はFunc_unformatted_ssn一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11562">The function Func_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11563">Keyword_ssn のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11563">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11564">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11564">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11565">関数 Func_randomized_formatted_ssn がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11565">The function Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11566">Keyword_ssn のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11566">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11567">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという信頼性が低いです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11567">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11568">関数 Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11568">The function Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11569">Keyword_ssn のキーワードを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11569">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>


```xml
<!-- U.S. Social Security Number (SSN) -->
  <Entity id="a44669fe-0d48-453d-a9b1-2cc83f2cba77" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_formatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="55">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
  </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11570">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11570">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11571">Keyword_ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11571">Keyword_ssn</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11572">SSA 番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11572">SSA Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11573">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11573">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11574">社会保障#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11574">social security #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11575">社会保障#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11575">social security#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11576">社会保障なし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11576">social security no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11577">Social Security#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11577">Social Security#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11578">Soc Sec</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11578">Soc Sec</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11579">SSN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11579">SSN</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11580">SSNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11580">SSNS</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11581">SSN#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11581">SSN#</span></span>

## <a name="us--uk-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11584">米国/英国</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11584">U.S. / U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11585">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11585">passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11586">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11586">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11587">9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11587">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11588">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11588">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11589">9 桁の連続する数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11589">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11590">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11590">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11591">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11591">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11592">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11592">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11593">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたと高い信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11593">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11594">関数 Func_usa_uk_passport がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11594">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11595">キーワードが見 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11595">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11596">キーワードが `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 見つかりました</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11596">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11597">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11597">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11598">関数 Func_usa_uk_passport がパターンに一致するコンテンツを検出した。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11598">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11599">キーワードが見 `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` つかったか、検索されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11599">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. / U.K. Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="178ec42a-18b4-47cc-85c7-d62c92fd67f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11600">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11600">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11601">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11601">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>
