- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11603">パスポート#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11603">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11604">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11604">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11605">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11605">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11606">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11606">passportno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11607">パスポートなし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11607">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11608">passportnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11608">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11609">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11609">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11610">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11610">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11611">パスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11611">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_uk_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11612">Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11612">Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11613">英国のパスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11613">british passport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11614">英国のパスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11614">uk passport</span></span>


## <a name="ukraine-passport-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11615">ウクライナのパスポート国内</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11615">Ukraine passport domestic</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11616">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11616">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11617">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11617">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11618">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11618">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11619">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11619">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11620">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11620">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11621">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11621">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11622">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11622">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11623">9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11623">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11624">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11624">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11625">9 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11625">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11626">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11626">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11627">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11627">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11628">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11628">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11629">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11629">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11630">正規表現はRegex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11630">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11631">このページのKeyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domesticが見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11631">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport Domestic -->
      <Entity id="1817a540-221f-4459-9202-3bd78b81d803" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11632">キーワード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11632">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ukraine_passport_domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11633">Keyword_ukraine_passport_domestic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11633">Keyword_ukraine_passport_domestic</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11634">ウクライナのパスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11634">ukraine passport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11635">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11635">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11636">パスポートなし</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11636">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11637">паспорт України</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11637">паспорт України</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11638">номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11638">номер паспорта</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11639">персональний</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11639">персональний</span></span>


## <a name="ukraine-passport-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11640">ウクライナのパスポート国際</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11640">Ukraine passport international</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11641">この機密情報の種類は、次の場所でのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11641">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11642">データ損失防止ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11642">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11643">通信コンプライアンス ポリシー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11643">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11644">情報ガバナンス</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11644">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11645">レコード管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11645">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11646">Microsoft クラウド アプリのセキュリティ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11646">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11647">フォーマット</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11647">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11648">8 文字の英数字パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11648">eight-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11649">パターン</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11649">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11650">8 文字の英数字パターン:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11650">eight-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11651">2 文字または数字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11651">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11652">6 桁</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11652">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11653">チェックサム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11653">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11654">いいえ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11654">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11655">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11655">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11656">DLP ポリシーは、次の 300 文字に近い場合に、この種類の機密情報が検出されたという中程度の信頼性を持っています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11656">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11657">正規表現はRegex_Ukraine_Passport_International一致するコンテンツを検索します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11657">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="7bb9c-11658">ユーザーからのキーワードKeyword_Ukraine_Passport_International見つかりました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bb9c-11658">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport International -->
      <Entity id="cfbe032d-22e0-4f28-ab68-d66e9641f1e2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
